# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-03-05 21:40

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:5
translate spanish d11a_26988442:

    # "A previous conversation with Ivy has left you with a few questions that keep nagging you."
    "Tras una conversación anterior con Ivy, te han quedado algunas preguntas que te siguen dando vueltas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:6
translate spanish d11a_41ccc986:

    # Zt "There she is..."
    Zt "Ahí está..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:9
translate spanish d11a_ee062801:

    # Zt "It looks like she's getting ready for guard duty."
    Zt "Parece que se está preparando para hacer la guardia."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:12
translate spanish d11a_cd6f70d3:

    # Z "Hey, Ivy. Do you have a moment?"
    Z "Ey, Ivy. ¿Tienes un momento?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:15
translate spanish d11a_0cf06034:

    # I "...?"
    I "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:18
translate spanish d11a_be4b6333:

    # Z "I wanted to speak to you again... about something you said when you came to see me, at night."
    Z "Quería volver a hablar contigo... sobre algo que dijiste cuando viniste a verme, por la noche."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:19
translate spanish d11a_d3a44fce:

    # Z "You told me you were concerned... Something about a friend of yours, and I don't really know what you meant by that."
    Z "Me dijiste que estabas preocupada... Algo sobre un amigo tuyo, y no sé muy bien qué querías decir con eso."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:22
translate spanish d11a_6dde1aa5:

    # Z "Do you want to help me understand?"
    Z "¿Quieres ayudarme a comprender?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:25
translate spanish d11a_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:29
translate spanish d11a_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:30
translate spanish d11a_924b4fef:

    # Z "We don't have to talk about it here."
    Z "No tenemos que hablar de ello aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:31
translate spanish d11a_955aacff:

    # Z "But you know where to find me, if you need to."
    Z "Pero sabes dónde encontrarme, si lo necesitas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:34
translate spanish d11a_052ff416:

    # "You start walking away..."
    "Empiezas a alejarte..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:40
translate spanish d11a_3677d5ae:

    # I "Wait."
    I "Espera."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:41
translate spanish d11a_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:44
translate spanish d11a_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:45
translate spanish d11a_9ec6d528:

    # "She looks at you with an air of mixed concern and relief..."
    "Te mira con un aire mezcla de preocupación y alivio..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:48
translate spanish d11a_c7757c03:

    # "You can tell from her hesitation, that she's struggling to find a way to express herself."
    "Puedes notar, por su vacilación, que está luchando por encontrar una forma de expresarse."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:49
translate spanish d11a_c46c4981:

    # "Has she ever used her actual voice, in this place?"
    "¿Ha utilizado alguna vez su voz real, en este lugar?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:52
translate spanish d11a_3d2c9be9:

    # I "Meet me outside, in three hours. Please don't tell anyone."
    I "Nos vemos fuera, en tres horas. Por favor, no se lo digas a nadie."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:55
translate spanish d11a_4496af15:

    # Z "I'll be there."
    Z "Allí estaré."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:60
translate spanish d11a_97ba7dec:

    # "Later...{w=1.5}{nw}"
    "Más tarde...{w=1.5}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:66
translate spanish d11a_668763b6:

    # "You cruise through several landscapes, each affected differently by the devastations of the past. Finally you reach the entrance to a cave and follow Ivy inside..."
    "Atraviesas varios paisajes, cada uno de ellos afectado de forma diferente por las devastaciones del pasado. Finalmente llegas a la entrada de una cueva y sigues a Ivy al interior..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:69
translate spanish d11a_4aeef7cb:

    # Z "Where are we?"
    Z "¿Dónde estamos?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:70
translate spanish d11a_73e9b862:

    # I "Follow me."
    I "Sígueme."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:73
translate spanish d11a_40473e53:

    # "As you head deeper into the cave, you are faced with a mixture of natural features and the remains of technological devices, sprawled across a faintly illuminated space."
    "Al adentrarte en la cueva, te encuentras con una mezcla de elementos naturales y restos de dispositivos tecnológicos, esparcidos por un espacio débilmente iluminado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:76
translate spanish d11a_67c21c7f:

    # Z "This... is your home?"
    Z "¿Esta... es tu casa?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:77
translate spanish d11a_bd16358d:

    # Z "But how do you live in here? Water... food."
    Z "¿Pero cómo se vive aquí? El agua... la comida."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:80
translate spanish d11a_9fad5571:

    # I "Follow me. The cave has a second entrance."
    I "Sígueme. La cueva tiene una segunda entrada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:83
translate spanish d11a_c4c8261b:

    # "You follow Ivy's footsteps, absorbing the layout and the features of this sprawling cave..."
    "Sigues los pasos de Ivy, absorbiendo la disposición y las características de esta extensa cueva..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:86
translate spanish d11a_0fd3074d:

    # "You reach the other entrance that she mentioned..."
    "Llegas a la otra entrada que ella te mencionó..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:90
translate spanish d11a_f44f7185:

    # Z "This place is incredible. From the other end of the cave, you'd never imagine this could exist... and this close to Zeta..."
    Z "Este lugar es increíble. Desde el otro extremo de la cueva, nunca imaginarías que esto pudiera existir, y tan cerca de Zeta..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:93
translate spanish d11a_dbe956cd:

    # I "We should go back inside. There's something else I need to show you."
    I "Deberíamos volver a entrar. Hay algo más que tengo que enseñarte."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:96
translate spanish d11a_d99fb79e:

    # Z "Lead the way."
    Z "Tú primero."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:101
translate spanish d11a_d9860dde:

    # "It quickly becomes apparent that the reason why you are here is not to admire the beauty of this unusual place, where the mist of Cairo and the blazing sun of the desert meet."
    "Rápidamente se hace evidente que la razón por la que estás aquí no es admirar la belleza de este lugar insólito, donde se unen la niebla del Cairo y el sol abrasador del desierto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:102
translate spanish d11a_2e9c3a57:

    # "In fact, the more you walk through the dark and blue shimmering tunnels of this place, the more it reminds you of other hideouts."
    "De hecho, cuanto más recorres los túneles oscuros y azules de este lugar, más te recuerda a otros escondites."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:103
translate spanish d11a_d7989208:

    # "The temperature is unexpectedly cool, the unusual blue lighting plays with the humidity creating a foggy film in the air."
    "La temperatura es inesperadamente fresca, la inusual iluminación azul juega con la humedad del aire creando creando un velo de niebla."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:104
translate spanish d11a_a2077d1b:

    # "If not for artificial lighting, you would be in utter darkness."
    "Si no fuera por la iluminación artificial, estarías en la más absoluta oscuridad."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:107
translate spanish d11a_3568ea9a:

    # "A construction of corrugated metal sheets stands jammed in the rock wall and you can't quite tell how old it might be."
    "Una construcción de chapas onduladas se encuentra encajada en la pared de roca y no se sabe muy bien qué antigüedad puede tener."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:108
translate spanish d11a_9bc99c85:

    # "For all the glimpses of technology from bygone eras that your eyes caught on the way to this corner of the cave, despite the more than adequate living quarters..."
    "A pesar de todos los atisbos de tecnología de épocas pasadas que tus ojos captaron en el camino hacia este rincón de la cueva, a pesar de la vivienda más que adecuada..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:109
translate spanish d11a_931f5d3c:

    # "...the place is still a cave, removed from civilized society, lost at the edges of an old world that tries to poison the new."
    "... el lugar sigue siendo una cueva, alejada de la sociedad civilizada, perdida en los límites de un mundo antiguo que intenta envenenar al nuevo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:110
translate spanish d11a_fdf8c4ec:

    # "Even so, you realize that such a prized secret is not revealed lightly. You doubt that anybody else in the Bunker is aware of its existence..."
    "Aun así, te das cuenta de que un secreto tan preciado no se revela a la ligera. Dudas que nadie más en el Búnker conozca su existencia..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:113
translate spanish d11a_35ec528d:

    # I "I need to change clothes. Can you wait for a few minutes?"
    I "Necesito cambiarme de ropa. ¿Puedes esperar unos minutos?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:116
translate spanish d11a_33b7e30d:

    # Z "Sure, I'll be here."
    Z "Claro, estaré aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:119
translate spanish d11a_fb4b2dfe:

    # I "You can have a look around, if you want."
    I "Puedes echar un vistazo, si quieres."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:122
translate spanish d11a_250986f3:

    # Z "Uh, sure, I will check the place out."
    Z "Uh, claro, comprobaré el lugar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:125
translate spanish d11a_ce15cd3a:

    # "As she enters her room, you wonder if she actually wants you to explore the place."
    "Al entrar en su habitación, te preguntas si realmente quiere que explores el lugar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:126
translate spanish d11a_fa4e58fb:

    # Zt "Why does she keep these devices around, anyway? It looks like scrap metal at best."
    Zt "¿Por qué tiene estos aparatos por aquí? En el mejor de los casos parece chatarra."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:129
translate spanish d11a_05126cd6:

    # "The devices look old and rusted. On the left, a bulk of unidentifiable scrap. Not even its screens are visible anymore."
    "Los aparatos parecen viejos y oxidados. A la izquierda, un bulto de chatarra inidentificable. Ya ni siquiera se ven sus pantallas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:130
translate spanish d11a_7dfffb27:

    # "On the right, something that looks like a case, next to an old radio transmitter."
    "A la derecha, algo que parece un maletín, junto a un viejo transmisor de radio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:131
translate spanish d11a_566af630:

    # "Even in their current state, these relics from the past bring up some unexpected memories."
    "Incluso en su estado actual, estas reliquias del pasado me traen recuerdos inesperados."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:132
translate spanish d11a_fc897a90:

    # "Some of these devices have demonstrated incredible staying power, surviving, abandoned and powerless, in all manner of places."
    "Algunos de estos dispositivos han demostrado una increíble capacidad de permanencia, sobreviviendo, abandonados y sin poder, en todo tipo de lugares."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:133
translate spanish d11a_ec8597a4:

    # "Forgotten over time, then found anew every so many decades and repaired by the scavengers of the day, usually in outposts far removed from Zeta..."
    "Olvidados con el tiempo, luego encontrados de nuevo cada tantas décadas y reparados por los carroñeros de turno, normalmente en puestos de avanzada muy alejados de Zeta..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:134
translate spanish d11a_3d040291:

    # "You yourself have explored a few of the earliest Stalker hideouts, that were equipped with original, if powerless, radio stations meant to create a communication network."
    "Tú mismo has explorado algunos de los primeros escondites de los Acechadores, que estaban equipados con originales, aunque impotentes, emisoras de radio destinadas a crear una red de comunicación."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:135
translate spanish d11a_4c7f9969:

    # "The man you now know as Lord Abrax had taught you about them and lamented how it would have served humanity if they had retained the knowledge to build and operate these devices, instead of letting them go to rot."
    "El hombre que ahora conoces como Lord Abrax te había enseñado acerca de ellos y se lamentaba de lo mucho que habría servido a la humanidad si hubieran conservado los conocimientos para construir y hacer funcionar estos dispositivos, en lugar de dejar que se pudrieran."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:138
translate spanish d11a_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:141
translate spanish d11a_3d4d7347:

    # I "You can sit down, [persistent.player_name]. Do you know how to start it up?"
    I "Puedes sentarte, [persistent.player_name]. ¿Sabes cómo se pone en marcha?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:144
translate spanish d11a_8df10f64:

    # Z "Start it up? What do you mean, the radio?"
    Z "¿Ponerlo en marcha? ¿Qué quieres decir, con la radio?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:147
translate spanish d11a_dd3913ae:

    # I "No. We don't need the transmitter today."
    I "No. Hoy no necesitamos el transmisor."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:150
translate spanish d11a_9fe1ebda:

    # I "The suitcase holds an old military device. We have been able to keep it running despite its age. Have you ever come across one of them?"
    I "En la maleta hay un viejo aparato militar. Hemos sido capaces de mantenerlo en funcionamiento a pesar de su antigüedad. ¿Te has encontrado alguna vez con uno de estos?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:151
translate spanish d11a_b7054bd5:

    # Z "Nothing in one piece or that actually worked, no..."
    Z "Ninguno de una sola pieza o que haya funcionado realmente, no..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:152
translate spanish d11a_bb65612a:

    # I "You can see for yourself."
    I "Puedes verlo por ti mismo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:155
translate spanish d11a_dfbc67e1:

    # Zt "I've seen the machines they have at the bunker, but I never expected that Ivy would just casually possess her own personal devices. Even just as an object of curiosity, these items have value. Could she still have a functioning one?"
    Zt "He visto las máquinas que tienen en el búnker, pero nunca esperé que Ivy poseyera casualmente sus propios dispositivos personales. Incluso como objeto de curiosidad, estos objetos tienen valor. ¿Podría tener todavía uno que funcione?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:156
translate spanish d11a_121bc005:

    # Zt "Is there such a device that can withstand the sands of time? It has been over 400 years since these things were commonplace..."
    Zt "¿Existe algún dispositivo que pueda resistir las arenas del tiempo? Han pasado más de 400 años desde que estas cosas eran comunes..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:157
translate spanish d11a_1b942170:

    # Zt "She is so casual about this. As if... it's nothing special to her."
    Zt "Está muy despreocupada por esto. Como si... no fuera nada especial para ella."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:160
translate spanish d11a_2a355841:

    # "You sit down. For the first time in years, you feel a sense of trepidation you have not felt since your first excursions into Old Cairo."
    "Te sientas. Por primera vez en años, sientes una sensación de inquietud que no habías sentido desde tus primeras incursiones en el Viejo Cairo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:163
translate spanish d11a_8e073645:

    # "You're careful. The case does have some rust damage and looks almost delicate."
    "Eres cuidadoso. El maletín tiene algunos daños por óxido y parece casi delicado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:166
translate spanish d11a_0b22c10a:

    # "Opening up the case, you see a damaged screen, more rusted surfaces, and what seems to be paint where there used to be a layout of buttons."
    "Al abrir el maletín, ves una pantalla rota, más superficies oxidadas y lo que parece ser pintura donde antes había una disposición de botones."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:167
translate spanish d11a_bc67c91e:

    # "Is she pulling a prank on you?"
    "¿Te está gastando una broma?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:170
translate spanish d11a_3498b9ff:

    # Z "It's not doing anything."
    Z "Esto no hace nada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:173
translate spanish d11a_60983abd:

    # I "Of course, this must be new to you, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Por supuesto, esto debe ser nuevo para ti, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:174
translate spanish d11a_db2547a4:

    # I "You have to press the \"On\" button on the top right."
    I "Tienes que pulsar el botón \"On\" de la parte superior derecha."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:175
translate spanish d11a_06635885:

    # Z "I've seen my share of old tech, but nothing on this level, and it was almost always unusable."
    Z "He visto mi parte de tecnología antigua, pero nada de este nivel, y casi siempre era inutilizable."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:178
translate spanish d11a_f65dfb2c:

    # "Without further ado, she guides your fingers to the button that she says activates the device..."
    "Sin más preámbulos, guía tus dedos hacia el botón que, según ella, activa el dispositivo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:185
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:188
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_dc515498:

    # "You hear the device booting up..."
    "Oyes que el aparato se pone en marcha..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:195
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_8d8472eb:

    # Z "Entries? Did you make some sort of diary?"
    Z "¿Entradas? ¿Has hecho algún tipo de diario?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:196
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_31063054:

    # I "Yes, you could say that... but a diary is written daily. I've written sparsely."
    I "Sí, se podría decir algo así... pero un diario se escribe a diario. Yo he escrito poco."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:197
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_790b1d1c:

    # I "Sometimes there are weeks or years in between the entries. Sometimes decades."
    I "A veces hay semanas o años entre las entradas. A veces, décadas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:198
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_436c245a:

    # Z "Decades? How..."
    Z "¿Décadas? Cómo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:201
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_81513eb9:

    # I "The reason why I brought you here is my friend. But first... I owe you a few more details."
    I "La razón por la que te he traído aquí es mi amiga. Pero antes... te debo algunos detalles más."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:202
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_3804531a:

    # I "There are things I want you to know, that happened long before the day we met in Old Cairo. Events going back to my life in the old tower."
    I "Hay cosas que quiero que sepas, que sucedieron mucho antes del día en que nos conocimos en el Viejo Cairo. Acontecimientos que se remontan a mi vida en la vieja torre."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:203
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_cbe04587:

    # I "Some of it is hard to believe, so that's why I would like you to read for yourself."
    I "Algunas cosas son difíciles de creer, por eso me gustaría que las leyeras por ti mismo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:206
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_e8ffe5c5:

    # Z "The tower; you mean the mutant bunker?"
    Z "La torre; ¿te refieres al búnker mutante?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:209
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_4721dfc0:

    # I "No... our old tower. In Old Cairo. Read on, it will answer some questions."
    I "No... nuestra vieja torre. En el Viejo Cairo. Sigue leyendo, responderá a algunas preguntas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:210
translate spanish d11a_computer_start_20f79551:

    # I "I will fill in the gaps later."
    I "Más tarde rellenaré los huecos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:223
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_802083b8:

    # "You close the device, sit back for a second and take in a few deep breaths."
    "Cierras el aparato, te sientas un segundo y respiras profundamente."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:226
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_11021fab:

    # Z "This is a lot to take in. The thing about your age alone is incredible."
    Z "Esto es mucho para asimilar. Sólo lo de tu edad es increíble."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:227
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_7878af3a:

    # Z "I can't even begin to think of the many questions you might be able to answer."
    Z "No puedo ni pensar en las muchas preguntas que podrías responder."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:228
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_d1e237fd:

    # Z "Hell, you basically were there for a good chunk of the history of our civilisation."
    Z "Diablos, básicamente estuviste allí durante una buena parte de la historia de nuestra civilización."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:229
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_77d8e742:

    # Z "And... You're still alive to tell the tale. Pretty remarkable."
    Z "Y... Sigues viva para contarlo. Bastante notable."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:232
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_032f52bf:

    # I "Our survival depended on isolating ourselves from the perils of the outside world."
    I "Nuestra supervivencia dependía de aislarnos de los peligros del mundo exterior."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:233
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_e21b4eab:

    # I "Most of what you might ask, I probably don't have an answer to."
    I "La mayor parte de lo que puedas preguntar, probablemente no tenga respuesta."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:236
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_70c944fd:

    # Z "Even so, you have given me a lot to think about."
    Z "Aun así, me has dado mucho que pensar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:239
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_09e49832:

    # I "I am aware. You understand now why I had to show you, rather than just tell you out of the blue?"
    I "Soy consciente. ¿Entiendes ahora por qué he tenido que mostrártelo, en lugar de decírtelo sin más?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:242
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_6b614832:

    # Z "Yes, of course."
    Z "Sí, por supuesto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:243
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_517e0278:

    # Z "I want some time to wrap my head around all of this information. If it's alright with you, I will stay the night."
    Z "Quiero algo de tiempo para asimilar toda esta información. Si te parece bien, me quedaré esta noche."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:246
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_463386ac:

    # I "I wasn't going to send you away this late. There's a bed inside. Make yourself comfortable."
    I "No iba a despedirte tan tarde. Hay una cama dentro. Ponte cómodo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:251
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_7ed63fb5:

    # "You do as she suggests, and you both turn away from the device. She goes outside, whilst you head to the shack..."
    "Haces lo que te sugiere, y ambos os apartáis del aparato. Ella sale al exterior, mientras tú te diriges a la cabaña..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:254
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_0c42c51b:

    # Zt "That was a lot to take in."
    Zt "Ha sido mucho para asimilar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:257
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_5dd3dfa6:

    # "You enter the shack..."
    "Entras en la cabaña..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:260
translate spanish d11a_computer_shutdown_4693f55d:

    # Zt "I wonder where she will sleep? Ah well..."
    Zt "Me pregunto dónde dormirá ella. Ah, bueno..."

