    "Al subir y buscar refugio en el interior, la emisión golpea inmediatamente después, con una intensidad que seguramente habría sido devastadora."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:589
translate spanish d11b_1b22ddcb:

    # "A few tells to catch a breath, then the pitch dark room brightens up. The natural fires from outside still looming..."
    "Unas pocas palabras para recuperar el aliento, y luego la habitación, totalmente oscura, se ilumina. Los fuegos naturales del exterior siguen asomando..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:593
translate spanish d11b_b169d27b:

    # S "{i}*pants*{/i} Thanks..."
    S "{i}*jadeando*{/i} Gracias..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:594
translate spanish d11b_97375427:

    # S "I... I didn't expect all of these buildings to be boarded up."
    S "Yo... No esperaba que todos estos edificios estuvieran tapiados."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:597
translate spanish d11b_587c0e96:

    # C6 "It's not fading, yet. You're not safe to go out for now."
    C6 "No se está disipando, aún. Por ahora no es seguro que salgas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:600
translate spanish d11b_f5d4a1b8:

    # "The girl sternly looks outside. Her white hair gleaming in the light, she seems to ignore the new visitor."
    "La chica mira con severidad al exterior. Con su pelo blanco brillando a la luz, parece ignorar a la nueva visitante."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:601
translate spanish d11b_a3e96765:

    # St "She seems to not pay a lot of attention to me. Does she not fear me going against her?"
    St "Parece que no me presta mucha atención. ¿No teme que vaya en su contra?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:602
translate spanish d11b_a3cd3584:

    # St "Do I look that harmless to her, or does she not care for her safety?"
    St "¿Le parezco tan inofensiva, o no se preocupa por su seguridad?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:605
translate spanish d11b_82e9ebc4:

    # S "Listen, I was on my way to the old factory, coming from the residential area."
    S "Escucha, iba de camino a la antigua fábrica, viniendo de la zona residencial."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:606
translate spanish d11b_eed3c04a:

    # S "Do you have an idea how to proceed from here? This place looks like some sort of train station. Do I just follow the rails?"
    S "¿Tienes alguna idea de cómo proceder a partir de aquí? Este lugar parece una especie de estación de tren. ¿Debo seguir los raíles?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:609
translate spanish d11b_39d318df:

    # "Her gaze is focused, but weary. Traces of dust and grime suggest she has been around here for some time. But for how long?"
    "Su mirada está concentrada, pero cansada. Los rastros de polvo y suciedad sugieren que lleva algún tiempo por aquí. ¿Pero cuánto tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:612
translate spanish d11b_15d0fbb7:

    # "She moves over to a candle-lit table..."
    "Se acerca a una mesa iluminada con velas..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:615
translate spanish d11b_8d00051d:

    # C6 "The rails are leading to a diversion. You will only detour on your path."
    C6 "Los raíles conducen a un desvío. Sólo te desviarán en tu camino."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:616
translate spanish d11b_289b85c1:

    # C6 "Behind this complex lies an open field."
    C6 "Detrás de este complejo hay un campo abierto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:619
translate spanish d11b_bca27ad9:

    # C6 "You can see the factory from the backside of this building."
    C6 "Puedes ver la fábrica desde la parte trasera de este edificio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:620
translate spanish d11b_e266b251:

    # C6 "I have not travelled this path yet, so you will be on your own."
    C6 "Todavía no he recorrido este camino, así que irás por tu cuenta."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:623
translate spanish d11b_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:624
translate spanish d11b_7155c801:

    # S "I see. I will be heading there then, as soon as the storm settles."
    S "Ya veo. Entonces me dirigiré allí, en cuanto se calme la tormenta."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:627
translate spanish d11b_a46b5bd3:

    # St "I should check my gear before moving on. I have been lucky this time."
    St "Debería comprobar mi equipo antes de seguir adelante. Esta vez he tenido suerte."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:630
translate spanish d11b_323780bc:

    # St "How did I make this mistake? I knew that emissions can occur without warning, depending on the energy released before them. And yet..."
    St "¿Cómo he podido cometer este error? Sabía que las emisiones pueden producirse sin previo aviso, dependiendo de la energía liberada antes de ellas. Y sin embargo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:644
translate spanish d11b_12a766cf:

    # St "Is that... a recording device? {w=3.5}{nw}"
    St "¿Es eso... un dispositivo de grabación? {w=3.5}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:647
translate spanish d11b_b2e6a33a:

    # S "Hey... do you... hear that?{w=3}{nw}"
    S "Oye... ¿oyes... eso? {w=3}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:648
translate spanish d11b_1446dd98:

    # C6 "...{w=2}{nw}"
    C6 "...{w=2}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:697
translate spanish d11b22_d24fcd69:

    # C6 "..."
    C6 "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:700
translate spanish d11b22_86b5e5ea:

    # "As she reads through the pages of a book, her expression turns to one of sorrow."
    "Mientras ella lee las páginas de un libro, su expresión se convierte en una de tristeza."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:701
translate spanish d11b22_8d4a5a90:

    # "Did she see what the device was showing or is she too focused on what she's reading...?"
    "¿Vio lo que mostraba el aparato o está demasiado concentrada en lo que está leyendo?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:704
translate spanish d11b22_fb457434:

    # S "I... did you also..."
    S "Yo... ¿tú también lo viste?..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:705
translate spanish d11b22_255a9a6f:

    # "She doesn't seem to react to the question. Whether she heard it or ignored it, remains unclear."
    "Ella no parece reaccionar a la pregunta. No está claro si la ha oído o la ha ignorado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:706
translate spanish d11b22_d5168195:

    # "Finally, she raises her head..."
    "Finalmente, levanta la cabeza..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:709
translate spanish d11b22_c5f4a3c7:

    # C6 "The emission is fading. It is safe for you to go now."
    C6 "La emisión se desvanece. Ahora puedes irte con seguridad."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:712
translate spanish d11b22_c00ee306:

    # S "I... see."
    S "Yo... ya veo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:713
translate spanish d11b22_3e6238ea:

    # St "Her expression... is unreadable. Does she intentionally ignore what I said? Did she even see what the device was showing? Did I just imagine all of it?"
    St "Su expresión... es ilegible. ¿Ignora intencionadamente lo que he dicho? ¿Ha visto siquiera lo que mostraba el aparato? ¿Me lo he imaginado todo?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:714
translate spanish d11b22_53f173e2:

    # St "I should do as she says... and leave. I am overstaying my welcome."
    St "Debería hacer lo que ella dice... y marcharme. Me estoy pasando de la raya."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:717
translate spanish d11b22_87e9f7ad:

    # C6 "As I said, the fields will lead you to your destination."
    C6 "Como he dicho, los campos te llevarán a tu destino."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:718
translate spanish d11b22_0aacc0ed:

    # C6 "Head back out, turn right. Follow the hallway. There is another scaffolding outside. You will see the factory from there."
    C6 "Vuelve a salir, gira a la derecha. Sigue el pasillo. Hay otro andamio en el exterior. Desde allí verás la fábrica."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:721
translate spanish d11b22_a1a1d811:

    # S "I will do that. Thank you for this. You saved my life. I was careless."
    S "Así lo haré. Gracias por esto. Me has salvado la vida. Me he descuidado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:724
translate spanish d11b22_1088b224:

    # S "You seem to know your way around this place. You have this room set up for you. Do you come here a lot?"
    S "Parece que sabes moverte por este lugar. Tienes esta habitación preparada para ti. ¿Vienes mucho por aquí?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:727
translate spanish d11b22_d24fcd69_1:

    # C6 "..."
    C6 "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:728
translate spanish d11b22_72ebdeb3:

    # "She looks away, seemingly uninterested in responding to the query..."
    "Mira hacia otro lado, aparentemente sin interés en responder a la pregunta..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:729
translate spanish d11b22_a456dce3:

    # St "Her ears... maybe that's the reason why she is that restrained. Maybe that is why she is hiding in this place?"
    St "Sus orejas... Tal vez esa sea la razón por la que está tan reservada. ¿Quizá por eso se esconde en este lugar?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:730
translate spanish d11b22_35910837:

    # St "I may never see her again. Should I let her know what I think?"
    St "Puede que no la vuelva a ver. ¿Debo hacerle saber lo que pienso?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:734
translate spanish d11b22_bd16e3a3:

    # S "Listen... you saved me, even though you didn't have to."
    S "Escucha... Me has salvado, aunque no tenías que hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:735
translate spanish d11b22_98ceeda1:

    # S "So thank you."
    S "Así que gracias."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:736
translate spanish d11b22_cfcca67c:

    # S "You seem a bit distraught, so, whatever you have going through your mind, I hope things work out for you."
    S "Pareces un poco angustiada, así que, sea lo que sea lo que te pase por la cabeza, espero que las cosas te vayan bien."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:737
translate spanish d11b22_dad087ee:

    # S "...Or maybe you just want to be left alone?"
    S "... ¿O tal vez sólo quieres que te dejen en paz?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:740
translate spanish d11b22_ca846d50:

    # S "I don't know you, and I don't know why you're hiding here, of all places. Why do this to yourself?"
    S "No te conozco, y no sé por qué te escondes aquí, entre todos los lugares. ¿Por qué te haces esto?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:741
translate spanish d11b22_8bcb100d:

    # S "I'm sure you're needed somewhere."
    S "Seguro que te necesitan en algún sitio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:742
translate spanish d11b22_43dfcac6:

    # S "Goodbye, and thank you."
    S "Adiós, y gracias."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:747
translate spanish d11b22_d24fcd69_2:

    # C6 "..."
    C6 "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:751
translate spanish d11b22_8dd4efd4:

    # C6 "There is nobody left for me. Now leave, and don't come back."
    C6 "No queda nadie para mí. Ahora vete y no vuelvas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:759
translate spanish d11b22_bdf6dd88:

    # S "Look... I... don't know you. But thank you for helping me out. You had no reason to but did it anyway."
    S "Mira... Yo... no te conozco. Pero gracias por ayudarme. No tenías ninguna razón para hacerlo, pero lo hiciste de todos modos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:760
translate spanish d11b22_05e35428:

    # S "But why would you stay here, of all places? You seemed to be a bit out of sorts, just now, reading those pages."
    S "Pero, ¿por qué te quedas aquí, de entre todos los lugares? Parecías estar un poco desorientado, justo ahora, leyendo esas páginas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:763
translate spanish d11b22_f88fdc38:

    # S "I hope you can pull yourself together and find your way out of here! Don't give in to this place."
    S "Espero que puedas recomponerte y encontrar la forma de salir de aquí. No te rindas ante este lugar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:768
translate spanish d11b22_d24fcd69_3:

    # C6 "..."
    C6 "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:772
translate spanish d11b22_f0883485:

    # C6 "You're not in a position to judge me. I have nobody left."
    C6 "No estás en condiciones de juzgarme. No me queda nadie."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:773
translate spanish d11b22_b180fb5c:

    # C6 "Now leave. And don't come back."
    C6 "Ahora vete. Y no vuelvas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:780
translate spanish d11b22_676595a6:

    # S "Anyways... I will be on my way."
    S "De todos modos... Voy a seguir mi camino."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:783
translate spanish d11b22_2e333acc:

    # S "Thank you again. And goodbye."
    S "Gracias de nuevo. Y adiós."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:794
translate spanish d11b27_7cbcf20c:

    # St "This place... It looks so peaceful."
    St "Este lugar... parece tan tranquilo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:797
translate spanish d11b27_42d97be8:

    # St "It's nothing like what was before."
    St "No se parece en nada a lo que había antes."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:800
translate spanish d11b27_ac5c610e:

    # "Walking downstairs..."
    "Bajando las escaleras..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:803
translate spanish d11b27_54fd312a:

    # St "The directions she gave me check out.. there it is."
    St "Las indicaciones que me dio lo verifican... ahí está."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:806
translate spanish d11b27_aa681cdf:

    # "The fog is resting atop the soft green grass, and the factory complex, described by the map paints a skyline against the horizon, in the distance."
    "La niebla descansa sobre la suave hierba verde, y el complejo de la fábrica, descrito por el mapa, pinta un horizonte, en la distancia."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:807
translate spanish d11b27_6172bb7e:

    # "The sky above has calmed, the clouds faded, and a hint of blue sky, mixed with the remains of the dusk like emission, emerges. The usual dark grey and grim atmosphere of the zone is brightened for a little while."
    "El cielo de arriba se ha calmado, las nubes se han desvanecido y emerge una pizca de cielo azul, mezclada con los restos de la emisión del crepúsculo. La habitual atmósfera gris oscura y lúgubre de la zona se ilumina por un momento."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:808
translate spanish d11b27_5b0919cb:

    # St "The sky... it's like I am on the verge of leaving the zone. And yet, I know that I am not. I wonder how long it will stay like this?"
    St "El cielo... es como si estuviera a punto de salir de la zona. Y, sin embargo, sé que no es así. Me pregunto cuánto tiempo permanecerá así."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:809
translate spanish d11b27_60e7adfd:

    # "Measuring the time needed to get to the factory, it is clear that..."
    "Midiendo el tiempo necesario para llegar a la fábrica, está claro que..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:810
translate spanish d11b27_c995e02d:

    # St "It's going to take some time to get there."
    St "Va a tardar un poco en llegar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:813
translate spanish d11b27_b56e2bce:

    # "Walking across the fields, the layer of fog that lies on this land becomes ever more evident."
    "Caminando por los campos, la capa de niebla que se extiende sobre esta tierra se hace cada vez más evidente."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:814
translate spanish d11b27_be95f557:

    # "The dominating view of the factory complex in the distance begins to slowly, but not entirely, fade in the background as the path leading to it becomes more difficult, with hills and vertical obstacles becoming the more pressing concern."
    "La vista dominante del complejo de la fábrica en la distancia comienza a desvanecerse lentamente, aunque no del todo, en el fondo, a medida que el camino que conduce a ella se vuelve más difícil, con colinas y obstáculos verticales que se convierten en la preocupación más acuciante."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:818
translate spanish d11b27_40f61313:

    # St "A... house?"
    St "¿Una... casa?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:821
translate spanish d11b27_b1382464:

    # St "Of all places..."
    St "De todos los lugares..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:824
translate spanish d11b27_d962e37a:

    # St "It's so tall..."
    St "Es tan alto..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:825
translate spanish d11b27_0507596e:

    # St "Does someone live here?"
    St "¿Vivirá aquí alguien?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:828
translate spanish d11b27_3efd0a7a:

    # "The big house emerges above the fog, its carefully placed wooden elements giving the impression of a well maintained large shack."
    "La gran casa emerge por encima de la niebla, sus elementos de madera cuidadosamente colocados ...dan la impresión de ser una gran choza bien cuidada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:829
translate spanish d11b27_67df6e51:

    # "Lamplights on the sides suggest that this building is indeed inhabited. But who could that be, out here, in the Zone?"
    "Las luces de los laterales sugieren que este edificio está efectivamente habitado. ¿Pero quién podría ser, aquí, en la Zona?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:830
translate spanish d11b27_3ec1216a:

    # St "Who would live here..."
    St "¿Quién viviría aquí..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:834
translate spanish d11b27_2a4e6e83:

    # St "This place doesn't seem dangerous, but I need to stay on alert. [persistent.dad!c] did mention that the mind would be challenged as much as the body, and this could all be an illusion."
    St "Este lugar no parece peligroso, pero tengo que estar alerta. [persistent.dad!c] mencionó que la mente sería desafiada tanto como el cuerpo, y todo esto podría ser una ilusión."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:837
translate spanish d11b27_cfebe685:

    # "Curiousity overcomes caution, finally, as the Factory still lies somewhere in the direction behind this house. It can wait."
    "La curiosidad supera a la cautela, finalmente, ya que la Fábrica aún se encuentra en algún lugar en la dirección detrás de esta casa. Puede esperar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:840
translate spanish d11b27_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:841
translate spanish d11b27_197358f1:

    # St "Barrels, a shovel. Lights..."
    St "Barriles, una pala. Luces..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:842
translate spanish d11b27_798e6ed2:

    # "Open windows letting the fog inside, but everything else - silent."
    "Las ventanas abiertas dejan pasar la niebla al interior, pero todo lo demás es silencio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:845
translate spanish d11b27_89de0645:

    # S "Is anyone here?"
    S "¿Hay alguien aquí?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:846
translate spanish d11b27_55426e4f:

    # St "This place seems empty. No sounds... except the cracking of the floor I'm stepping on."
    St "Este lugar parece vacío. No hay sonidos... Excepto el crujido del suelo que piso."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:847
translate spanish d11b27_2dd7bc4c:

    # C2 "H-hello...? Is that... one moment!"
    C2 "¿H-hola...? Es que... ¡un momento!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:850
translate spanish d11b27_540c9883:

    # "Turning around, the voice came from this direction. A feminine, high pitched voice, surprised and curious in its tone. But also... excited?"
    "Al darse la vuelta, la voz procedía de esta dirección. Una voz femenina y aguda, con un tono de sorpresa y curiosidad. Pero también... ¿excitada?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:853
translate spanish d11b27_8e96276c:

    # "Stepping closer..."
    "Acercándose más..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:854
translate spanish d11b27_0b295280:

    # C2 "Please, don't leave. Give me one second, I will be..."
    C2 "Por favor, no te vayas. Dame un segundo, voy a..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:857
translate spanish d11b27_03663ca2:

    # "A door opens, a light giving it away. Footsteps can be heard... soft ones, almost shyly entering the room that is in front..."
    "Una puerta se abre, una luz la delata. Se oyen pasos... suaves, que entran casi tímidamente en la habitación que hay delante..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:860
translate spanish d11b27_54bb379d:

    # C2 "Are you... a visitor?"
    C2 "¿Eres... un visitante?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:863
translate spanish d11b27_a9584ac9:

    # C2 "Oh my... you are!"
    C2 "Oh, Dios... ¡lo eres!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:864
translate spanish d11b27_f75b75b6:

    # "The woman appearing seems surprised, and her expression suggests that her surprise is genuine."
    "La mujer que aparece parece sorprendida, y su expresión sugiere que su sorpresa es genuina."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:865
translate spanish d11b27_6521a346:

    # "Her green eyes light up in excitement, and her hesitation fades..."
    "Sus ojos verdes se iluminan de emoción, y su vacilación se desvanece..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:868
translate spanish d11b27_32b9f70e:

    # C2 "You must be a wanderer! I am Julia. I live here."
    C2 "¡Debes de ser una vagabunda! Soy Julia. Vivo aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:869
translate spanish d11b27_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:872
translate spanish d11b27_1d44878c:

    # Ju "I know, you surely must have a lot of questions. But I'm so happy to see another person out here."
    Ju "Lo sé, seguramente debes tener muchas preguntas. Pero estoy muy contenta de ver a otra persona por aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:875
translate spanish d11b27_2e6ad490:

    # Ju "You look a bit stressed. Please stay for a while, I will be a good host and prepare a meal. What do you say? You must be hungry."
    Ju "Pareces un poco estresada. Por favor, quédate un rato, seré una buena anfitriona y prepararé una comida. ¿Qué dices? Debes de tener hambre."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:876
translate spanish d11b27_f89d54fa:

    # Ju "You can put your belongings in the shelf on the right. It's safe with me. I will be waiting in the dining room!"
    Ju "Puedes poner tus pertenencias en la estantería de la derecha. Están a salvo conmigo. Te espero en el comedor."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:879
translate spanish d11b27_41cc450e:

    # St "She... seems genuine. I have many questions... but she's right. I am stressed. Breathe [S], let's see where this goes..."
    St "Ella... parece auténtica. Tengo muchas preguntas... pero tiene razón. Estoy estresada. Respira [S], veamos a dónde va esto..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:882
translate spanish d11b27_d6612254:

    # Ju "Please, take a seat. I have just the right thing for you."
    Ju "Por favor, toma asiento. Tengo lo que necesitas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:885
translate spanish d11b27_8dc10ffa:

    # Ju "I'm going to make you a soup. Everything's home grown, too! What do you say?"
    Ju "Voy a prepararte una sopa. ¡Todo es casero, además! ¿Qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:888
translate spanish d11b27_41b68375:

    # S "That... sounds good?"
    S "Eso... ¿suena bien?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:891
translate spanish d11b27_dbc6afec:

    # Ju "The table is set for one; myself actually, but I ate not long ago and I am not very hungry lately, so... have a seat."
    Ju "La mesa está preparada para uno; en realidad, para mí, pero he comido hace poco y últimamente no tengo mucha hambre, así que... toma asiento."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:894
translate spanish d11b27_7601c835:

    # "Doing as is requested of her..."
    "Haces lo que se te pide..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:895
translate spanish d11b27_a7af3d4e:

    # Ju "I hope you're ready for a hearty meal. When I was on my travels, I always used to have them. A healthy appetite, I called it. But I can only speak for myself."
    Ju "Espero que estés preparada para una comida abundante. Cuando estaba de viaje, siempre solía comerlas. Un apetito saludable, lo llamaba yo. Pero sólo puedo hablar por mí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:896
translate spanish d11b27_ff135678:

    # S "Yes, I would like to. I have been walking for some time."
    S "Sí, me gustaría. Llevo un tiempo caminando."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:897
translate spanish d11b27_02f9a923:

    # Ju "Oh, you must come from the residential area then?"
    Ju "Oh, ¿entonces debes venir de la zona residencial?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:898
translate spanish d11b27_121b8842:

    # S "Yes, how do you know?"
    S "Sí, ¿cómo lo sabes?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:899
translate spanish d11b27_b22f07c9:

    # Ju "Oh, it's just a long way to where I live. That's all."
    Ju "Oh, es un largo camino hasta donde vivo. Eso es todo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:900
translate spanish d11b27_1f7eebf2:

    # Ju "Whenever my partner and I headed there to stock up, we had to walk all the way up there. So I know how long it takes. {i}*giggles*"
    Ju "Cada vez que mi compañero y yo nos dirigíamos allí para abastecernos, teníamos que ir andando. Así que sé lo que se tarda. {i}*risas*"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:901
translate spanish d11b27_6d1e69fa:

    # S "You have a partner? Does he live here, too?"
    S "¿Tienes pareja? ¿También vive aquí?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:904
translate spanish d11b27_5f4b5e58:

    # Ju "Oh, yes. But he's outside for some time now. We did not come here to settle down, originally. But... you know."
    Ju "Ah, sí. Pero hace tiempo que está fuera. No hemos venido aquí para establecernos, originalmente. Pero... ya sabes."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:905
translate spanish d11b27_c358ea70:

    # Ju "He always said he's just like his mother. Can't really settle down for so long, always up for the next challenge."
    Ju "Él siempre dice que es como su madre. No puede establecerse durante mucho tiempo, siempre está preparado para el siguiente reto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:906
translate spanish d11b27_deb8789e:

    # Ju "So thats why we were always on the move. Work here, live there, explore this place and make plans for the next. He is currently out there."
    Ju "Por eso siempre estamos en movimiento. Trabajar aquí, vivir allí, explorar este lugar y hacer planes para el siguiente. Actualmente está fuera."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:909
translate spanish d11b27_89b0298a:

    # Ju "Here, this should fill you up nicely. I hope you enjoy it!"
    Ju "Toma, esto debería llenarte bien. Espero que lo disfrutes."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:910
translate spanish d11b27_85a335ce:

    # S "Thank you, that looks amazing."
    S "Gracias, tiene una pinta estupenda."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:913
translate spanish d11b27_023bb872:

    # "She sits down..."
    "Ella se sienta..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:916
translate spanish d11b27_11d68d87:

    # Ju "Anyways, look at me. I'm getting a visitor after so long and all I do is talk about myself."
    Ju "De todos modos, mírame. Recibo una visita después de tanto tiempo y lo único que hago es hablar de mí misma."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:917
translate spanish d11b27_c0c27186:

    # Ju "Where are you headed to? It seems that you've been walking for some time?"
    Ju "¿Adónde te diriges? ¿Parece que llevas un rato caminando?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:920
translate spanish d11b27_223d62f0:

    # S "I am heading to the old factory. I was told that there were interesting things to be found there... but I still don't know quite what to look for, exactly."
    S "Me dirijo a la antigua fábrica. Me han dicho que allí se pueden encontrar cosas interesantes... Pero todavía no sé exactamente qué es lo que hay que buscar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:921
translate spanish d11b27_e2606a56:

    # S "You can probably see it from here?"
    S "¿Probablemente puedas verla desde aquí?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:924
translate spanish d11b27_62aeb7f5:

    # Ju "Ah, yes, I see. I'm sure you will find what you're looking for!"
    Ju "Ah, sí, la veo. Estoy segura de que encontrarás lo que buscas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:927
translate spanish d11b27_2172024a:

    # Ju "That reminds me... are you sure that you want to go today?"
    Ju "Eso me recuerda... ¿estás segura de que quieres ir hoy?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:928
translate spanish d11b27_f3345845:

    # Ju "It's getting late already. You've been on the road. I have a free bed for you, if you want it."
    Ju "Ya se está haciendo tarde. Has estado en camino. Tengo una cama gratis para ti, si la quieres."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:929
translate spanish d11b27_fd2fbe3f:

    # Ju "Maybe you could stay the night?"
    Ju "¿Tal vez puedas pasar la noche?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:930
translate spanish d11b27_05ed605c:

    # Ju "We could get to know each other a little better. It's rare to find anyone out here you can talk with!"
    Ju "Podríamos conocernos un poco mejor. Es raro encontrar aquí a alguien con quien puedas hablar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:933
translate spanish d11b27_a8846467:

    # S "I don't know... I found a safe place... but it is a bit far away... and I have not even reached my destination yet..."
    S "No sé... He encontrado un lugar seguro... pero está un poco lejos... y aún no he llegado a mi destino..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:936
translate spanish d11b27_6db2dbd5:

    # Ju "Let me help you out then, please!"
    Ju "Deja que te ayude entonces, por favor."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:939
translate spanish d11b27_76360a30:

    # "She gets up..."
    "Se levanta..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:942
translate spanish d11b27_3926d06f:

    # Ju "That is, of course, after you're done eating. Take your time."
    Ju "Es decir, por supuesto, después de que hayas terminado de comer. Tómate tu tiempo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:945
translate spanish d11b27_5d29e308:

    # Ju "Forgive me if I seem a little much. I really mean it when I say that I've not seen anyone else in a long time now."
    Ju "Perdóname si parezco un poco exagerada. Lo digo en serio cuando digo que hace mucho tiempo que no veo a nadie más."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:946
translate spanish d11b27_35c25f4d:

    # Ju "{i}*laughs*{/i} It's not like these steppes are in any way inviting."
    Ju "{i}*risas*{/i} No es que estas estepas sean en absoluto acogedoras."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:947
translate spanish d11b27_b605a643:

    # Ju "Can I ask how to call you? Your name maybe?"
    Ju "¿Puedo preguntar cómo llamarte? ¿Tal vez tu nombre?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:950
translate spanish d11b27_d3e729b2:

    # S "You can call me [S]."
    S "Puedes llamarme [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:953
translate spanish d11b27_ce03d16a:

    # Ju "Hi [S]. That's such a pretty name."
    Ju "Hola [S]. Qué nombre tan bonito."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:955
translate spanish d11b27_bb38ad9f:

    # Ju "It's so unique, too!"
    Ju "También es tan único."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:956
translate spanish d11b27_a1ec1cf6:

    # Ju "Let me know when you're ready. I will prepare the bed for you."
    Ju "Avísame cuando estés lista. Prepararé la cama para ti."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:959
translate spanish d11b27_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Pasado un tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:962
translate spanish d11b27_725caa4e:

    # Ju "Hey. I hope I did good with the meal. Follow me, [S]."
    Ju "Ey. Espero haberlo hecho bien con la comida. Sígueme, [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:965
translate spanish d11b27_6befc08a:

    # "Following the host, the old wood squeaks underneath each step..."
    "Siguiendo a la anfitrina, la vieja madera chirría a cada paso..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:968
translate spanish d11b27_68852b60:

    # Ju "[S], do you mind a slight breeze while you sleep?"
    Ju "[S], ¿te molesta una ligera brisa mientras duermes?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:969
translate spanish d11b27_25573421:

    # Ju "I don't think it's going to be any worse tonight. The weather looks calm."
    Ju "No creo que vaya a ser peor esta noche. El tiempo parece tranquilo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:970
translate spanish d11b27_9136f30e:

    # S "Thank you, it's fine. I'm used to much worse."
    S "Gracias, está bien. Estoy acostumbrada a cosas mucho peores."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:971
translate spanish d11b27_b3da6778:

    # Ju "I see. I'm not sure if that's a good thing. {i}*chuckles*{/i}"
    Ju "Ya veo. No estoy segura de que eso sea algo bueno. {i}*risilla*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:974
translate spanish d11b27_38a5c29e:

    # Ju "The bed is made. I don't use it usually. This is my partner's study."
    Ju "La cama está hecha. No la suelo utilizar. Es el estudio de mi pareja."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:975
translate spanish d11b27_202d4498:

    # Ju "But since he isn't here, it's all yours!"
    Ju "Pero como no está aquí, ¡es todo tuya!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:978
translate spanish d11b27_a12c2d33:

    # Ju "Oh, and I hope you don't mind all his stuff. Kirill collects texts of all sorts."
    Ju "Ah, y espero que no te molesten todas sus cosas. Kirill colecciona textos de todo tipo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:979
translate spanish d11b27_04e56529:

    # Ju "You can read them if you need some help falling asleep."
    Ju "Puedes leerlos si necesitas ayuda para conciliar el sueño."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:980
translate spanish d11b27_26cbbd3c:

    # Ju "Do you enjoy reading?"
    Ju "¿Te gusta leer?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:983
translate spanish d11b27_46d4c6ab:

    # S "Yes, I really do. It helps me unwind a bit before sleeping."
    S "Sí, de verdad. Me ayuda a relajarme un poco antes de dormir."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:984
translate spanish d11b27_9de1fd0a:

    # S "Will you be going to bed as well?"
    S "¿Tú también te vas a la cama?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:987
translate spanish d11b27_1467aa48:

    # Ju "I am not tired yet. I didn't do much today. But don't worry, I'll be up when you are for sure."
    Ju "Todavía no estoy cansada. Hoy no he hecho mucho. Pero no te preocupes, seguro que me levantaré cuando tú lo hagas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:988
translate spanish d11b27_e02b95c9:

    # Ju "Sleep well for now, [S]. Hope to see you tomorrow!"
    Ju "Duerme bien por ahora, [S]. Espero verte mañana."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:991
translate spanish d11b27_c827ed34:

    # S "Thank you for everything, [Ju]. I will stay the night and then head out tomorrow."
    S "Gracias por todo, [Ju]. Me quedaré esta noche y me iré mañana."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:994
translate spanish d11b27_3224f15d:

    # Ju "We'll see. Maybe we can spend some time before you head out. Anyways, good night!"
    Ju "Ya veremos. Quizá podamos pasar un rato antes de que te vayas. De todos modos, ¡buenas noches!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:997
translate spanish d11b27_17f454a4:

    # "She leaves the room..."
    "Sale de la habitación..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1000
translate spanish d11b27_8f6494bc:

    # St "This almost looks like [persistent.dad]'s library. Is Kirill also a Stalker?"
    St "Esto casi parece la biblioteca de [persistent.dad]. ¿Kirill también es un Acechador?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1001
translate spanish d11b27_7ecd4f3d:

    # St "She said they're on the road a lot. But how is she so trusting, to live like this, so remote and in the heart of a Zone?"
    St "Dice que viajan mucho. ¿Pero cómo es tan confiada, para vivir así, tan alejada y en el corazón de una Zona?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1002
translate spanish d11b27_964fdcd3:

    # St "Maybe this place is isolated from the dangers, somehow. I should ask..."
    St "Tal vez este lugar esté aislado de los peligros, de alguna manera. Debería preguntar..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1005
translate spanish d11b27_362c8f90:

    # "Browsing over the pages, a few words stick out..."
    "Al hojear las páginas, algunas palabras sobresalen..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1006
translate spanish d11b27_3f2db4e5:

    # "\"{i}The problem is we don’t notice the years pass, he thought. Screw the years— we don’t notice things change.{/i}\""
    "\"{i}El problema es que no nos damos cuenta de que los años pasan, pensaba. Que pasen los años, no nos damos cuenta de que las cosas cambian.{/i}\""

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1007
translate spanish d11b27_857f3697:

    # "\"{i}We know that things change, we’ve been told since childhood that things change, we’ve witnessed things change ourselves many a time, and yet we’re still utterly incapable of noticing the moment that change comes...{/i}\""
    "\"{i}Sabemos que las cosas cambian, nos han dicho desde la infancia que las cosas cambian, hemos sido testigos nosotros mismos de que las cosas cambian muchas veces, y sin embargo seguimos siendo totalmente incapaces de darnos cuenta en el momento en que se produce el cambio.{/i}\""

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1008
translate spanish d11b27_26de434b:

    # "\"{i}...or we search for change in all the wrong places.{/i}\""
    "\"{i}...o buscamos el cambio en todos los lugares equivocados.{/i}\""

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1009
translate spanish d11b27_d6828644:

    # St "I wonder who wrote this?"
    St "Me pregunto quién habrá escrito esto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1010
translate spanish d11b27_7a7bef49:

    # St "Anyways. I should sleep. I'm very tired."
    St "De todos modos. Debería dormir. Estoy muy cansada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1013
translate spanish d11b27_ac855c34:

    # "The day ends with a few more pages of light reading.."
    "El día termina con unas cuantas páginas más de lectura ligera.."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1016
translate spanish d11b27_81690c99:

    # St "The fog is so thick, I can't even see anything outside the window."
    St "La niebla es tan espesa que ni siquiera puedo ver nada fuera de la ventana."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1019
translate spanish d11b27_923323a8:

    # St "I'm still curious as to why and how she lives here."
    St "Todavía tengo curiosidad por saber por qué y cómo vive aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1020
translate spanish d11b27_c38b5478:

    # St "I should ask her tomorrow about this place."
    St "Debería preguntarle mañana sobre este lugar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1023
translate spanish d11b27_3eb95b70:

    # St "And then I will... head out to the... factory... and find..."
    St "Y luego... me dirigiré a la... fábrica... y encontraré..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1026
translate spanish d11b27_eabb9359:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1029
translate spanish d11b27_33a46fdf_1:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Pasado un tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1032
translate spanish d11b27_eabb9359_1:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1033
translate spanish d11b27_f5c61009:

    # St "Is it morning already? I can't tell..."
    St "¿Ya es de día? No lo sé..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1036
translate spanish d11b27_cf1b9d2d:

    # St "It must be. I should get up."
    St "Debe de ser así. Debería levantarme."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1037
translate spanish d11b27_6f0b60d0:

    # St "How long did I sleep for..."
    St "¿Cuánto tiempo he dormido..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1040
translate spanish d11b27_dd675c02:

    # St "It feels like I slept for days."
    St "Me parece que he dormido durante días."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1041
translate spanish d11b27_6b938c1f:

    # St "The bed was too comfortable. If only we had such a nice bed at home."
    St "La cama era demasiado cómoda. Si sólo tuviéramos una cama tan bonita en casa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1044
translate spanish d11b27_5ded63a7:

    # St "Alright, time to go."
    St "Muy bien, es hora de irse."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1047
translate spanish d11b27_cc66107e:

    # "Moving towards the kitchen..."
    "Avanzando hacia la cocina..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1050
translate spanish d11b27_e1fab52e:

    # S "Good morning, [Ju]. I think I overslept."
    S "Buenos días, [Ju]. Creo que me he quedado dormida."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1053
translate spanish d11b27_1ff3dbbd:

    # Ju "Oh, hey [S]. You didn't. Not really. Come, sit down. I was preparing breakfast for you."
    Ju "Oh, ey [S]. No lo has hecho. La verdad es que no. Ven, siéntate. Estaba preparando el desayuno para ti."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1056
translate spanish d11b27_76004e49:

    # S "Are you sure? I need to get going and thought-"
    S "¿Estás segura? Tengo que ponerme en marcha y pienso..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1057
translate spanish d11b27_73d2bed3:

    # Ju "Ah [S], you're too polite. It's not like you're a burden around here."
    Ju "Ah [S], eres demasiado educada. No es que seas una carga por aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1058
translate spanish d11b27_545be041:

    # Ju "I'm sure you have time for a breakfast at least, right?"
    Ju "Seguro que tienes tiempo para desayunar al menos, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1059
translate spanish d11b27_034a78f4:

    # S "Yeah, that's true."
    S "Sí, eso es cierto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1062
translate spanish d11b27_43f77156:

    # "At the table..."
    "En la mesa..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1065
translate spanish d11b27_c686e5ed:

    # Ju "I hope I'm not getting on your nerves, but are you really in a rush?"
    Ju "Espero no ponerte de los nervios, pero ¿realmente tienes prisa?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1066
translate spanish d11b27_c4466797:

    # Ju "You see, I was thinking that I might not see you again, and I'm a bit lonely here, without Kirill."
    Ju "Verás, estaba pensando que quizá no te vuelva a ver, y me siento un poco sola aquí, sin Kirill."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1069
translate spanish d11b27_0da70772:

    # Ju "Anyway, here we go, enjoy!"
    Ju "De todos modos, aquí vamos, ¡disfruta!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1070
translate spanish d11b27_db60b7a1:

    # S "Thank you."
    S "Gracias."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1071
translate spanish d11b27_79468058:

    # S "So, you were saying?"
    S "Entonces, ¿decías?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1074
translate spanish d11b27_18cc8a8b:

    # Ju "Yes, I was saying... I've been kind of alone for some time now, and maybe I can show you around a little? It's really pretty here."
    Ju "Sí, decía... Hace tiempo que estoy un poco sola, y tal vez pueda enseñarte un poco el lugar. Esto es muy bonito."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1075
translate spanish d11b27_9e885de7:

    # Ju "You can always continue your travels a day later, what do you think?"
    Ju "Siempre puedes continuar tu viaje un día después, ¿qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1080
translate spanish d11b27_0adad7d0:

    # S "I... am not in a real hurry, no. You're right. I can stay for a bit."
    S "Yo... no tengo mucha prisa, no. Tienes razón. Puedo quedarme un rato."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1083
translate spanish d11b27_3794c995:

    # Ju "That's great. I will wait outside. Just exit the house from your room and take a right around the house."
    Ju "Eso es genial. Esperaré fuera. Sal de la casa desde tu habitación y gira a la derecha alrededor de la casa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1084
translate spanish d11b27_956868dd:

    # Ju "Feel free to come outside whenever you're ready!"
    Ju "¡Siéntete libre de salir cuando estés preparada!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1090
translate spanish d11b27_90c7196b:

    # S "I... appreciate it, [Ju]. But I am here for a short time, so I need to complete the mission and then head back home."
    S "Yo... te lo agradezco, [Ju]. Pero estoy aquí por poco tiempo, así que necesito completar la misión y luego volver a casa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1093
translate spanish d11b27_78b4ebe5:

    # Ju "I see. I understand. I guess that living in a place such as this is not for everybody, and that with it comes some sacrifice."
    Ju "Ya veo. Lo entiendo. Supongo que vivir en un lugar como éste no es para todo el mundo, y que con ello viene algún sacrificio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1096
translate spanish d11b27_7867a49d:

    # Ju "Let me know when you finished your meal. I will do a few chores, [S]."
    Ju "Avísame cuando hayas terminado la comida. Haré algunas tareas, [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1103
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Pasado un tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1106
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_65558a70:

    # St "These meals are so filling. Okay, let's head outside. I... suppose I don't need my gear?"
    St "Estas comidas me llenan mucho. Bien, salgamos fuera. Yo... supongo que no necesito mi equipo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1109
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_148916cd:

    # St "Outside... and right..."
    St "Fuera... y a la derecha..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1112
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_0e44c7fc:

    # S "Julia, are you here? I..."
    S "Julia, ¿estás aquí? Yo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1115
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_b20d9141:

    # S "Wow... how did I miss that...?"
    S "Vaya... ¿Cómo me he perdido eso?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1120
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_b2e4d73a:

    # S "[Ju], when I arrived, I didn't see this...{w=4}{nw}"
    S "[Ju], cuando visité, no vi esto...{w=4}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1121
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_e30293b4:

    # S "I... have never seen a tree this big, and these colours!{w=6}{nw}"
    S "Yo... ¡nunca había visto un árbol tan grande, y con estos colores!{w=6}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1122
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_4ba09145:

    # Ju "It's impressive, isn't it? It was the reason why we settled here, despite how remote it is from... everything.{w=7}{nw}"
    Ju "Es impresionante, ¿verdad? Fue la razón por la que nos instalamos aquí, a pesar de lo alejado que está de... todo.{w=7}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1123
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_bf81b5ff:

    # S "I need to ask, how does something like this exist out here? With everything that's around?{w=4}{nw}"
    S "Tengo que preguntar, ¿cómo puede existir algo así aquí? ¿Con todo lo que hay alrededor?{w=4}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1127
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_bd29244d:

    # S "How do you live without much of a care or worry, with all the dangers that surround you?"
    S "¿Cómo se puede vivir sin mucho cuidado o preocupación, con todos los peligros que te rodean?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1128
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_6bed46ad:

    # S "You must've seen everything that lays behind. But everything here is so different!"
    S "Debes haber visto todo lo que hay detrás. Pero aquí todo es muy diferente."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1131
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_2e244dd2:

    # Ju "I am not sure, [S]. But Kirill reads a lot, and he always reminds me of that favourite verse of his."
    Ju "No estoy segura, [S]. Pero Kirill lee mucho, y siempre me recuerda ese verso suyo favorito."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1132
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_32cd651f:

    # Ju "He said that when we are born, we are soft and pliable. And that when we die, we are hard and insensitive. When a tree grows, it's tender and pliant. But when it's dry and hard, it dies."
    Ju "Dijo que cuando nacemos, somos blandos y flexibles. Y que cuando morimos, somos duros e insensibles. Cuando un árbol crece, es tierno y flexible. Pero cuando está seco y duro, muere."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1133
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_50b6d912:

    # Ju "He said hardness and strength are death's companions. Flexibility and softness are the embodiment of life... because what has hardened will never win."
    Ju "Dijo que la dureza y la fuerza son compañeras de la muerte. La flexibilidad y la suavidad son la encarnación de la vida... Porque lo que se ha endurecido nunca ganará."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1136
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_b57ca42b:

    # Ju "Not even out here, [S]. And that is why we chose this place."
    Ju "Ni siquiera aquí, [S]. Y por eso hemos elegido este lugar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1139
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_b43b36f2:

    # Ju "I don't know what made it grow so tall, but I visit it every day. It helps me get by, you know..."
    Ju "No sé qué le ha hecho crecer tanto, pero lo visito todos los días. Me ayuda a salir adelante, ya sabes..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1142
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_0c927dfc:

    # S "That is... a nice saying."
    S "Eso es... un bonito dicho."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1143
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_a168e101:

    # S "I guess some places just live by their own rules."
    S "Supongo que algunos lugares viven según sus propias reglas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1144
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_4c602a72:

    # Ju "They do. And the more places you visit, the more there is to see, and the more you will find this to be true."
    Ju "Lo hacen. Y cuantos más lugares visites, más habrá que ver, y más comprobarás que esto es cierto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1145
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_37cb32be:

    # S "Have you visited a lot of places with him?"
    S "¿Ha visitado muchos lugares con él?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1146
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_fe217b3f:

    # Ju "Yes! We have! I wish I had a map somewhere, but we went to so many places. Have you ever heard about the Jebel Marra? That one fascinated me!"
    Ju "¡Sí! ¡Lo hemos hecho! Ojalá tuviera un mapa en alguna parte, pero fuimos a muchos sitios. ¿Has oído hablar del Jebel Marra? ¡Ese me fascinó!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1147
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_660d0d63:

    # S "No, I haven't. What is it?"
    S "No, no lo he hecho. ¿Qué pasa?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1148
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_2758367e:

    # Ju "I will tell you, but do you want to go inside? We can prepare food for later, and I can tell you more about it?"
    Ju "Te lo diré, pero ¿quieres entrar? ¿Podemos preparar la comida para más tarde y te puedo contar más cosas?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1149
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_43dcd5e3:

    # S "Okay, let's go."
    S "Vale, vamos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1152
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_cbdd60b1:

    # "Eventually..."
    "Finalmente..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1155
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_2905f1d4:

    # S "[Ju], where do you get these vegetables from, anyway?!"
    S "[Ju], ¿de dónde sacas estas verduras?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1156
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_bb771637:

    # Ju "I am growing them here. It takes some effort, but the soil is good!"
    Ju "Los estoy cultivando aquí. Me cuesta un poco de esfuerzo, pero la tierra es buena."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1159
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_f6b5ba06:

    # S "I got you. They're heavy."
    S "Te entiendo. Son pesadas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1162
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_881dea28:

    # S "Now, about the Jebel Marra again? What and where is it?"
    S "Ahora, ¿otra vez sobre el Jebel Marra? ¿Qué es y dónde está?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1163
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_beb6b64f:

    # Ju "Okay, imagine this: a huge volcano, erupting so many times that the crater spans over 3000 meters."
    Ju "Vale, imagina esto: un enorme volcán, que entra en erupción tantas veces que el cráter se extiende más de 3000 metros."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1164
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_b22ab349:

    # S "A volcano? Whoa... I wish I could see one in real life. I have only read about them."
    S "¿Un volcán? Guau... Ojalá pudiera ver uno en la vida real. Sólo he leído sobre ellos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1167
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_09cc6c5e:

    # Ju "You never saw one? I wish I could be there when you do, then!"
    Ju "¿Nunca has visto uno? ¡Ojalá pudiera estar allí cuando lo hagas, entonces!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1168
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_7b223aa8:

    # Ju "When Kirill brought me there, it was both magical and terrifying."
    Ju "Cuando Kirill me llevó allí, fue mágico y aterrador a la vez."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1171
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_14e3fe67:

    # Ju "I think that should be enough, I will get the stove ready. Do you want to help?"
    Ju "Creo que debería ser suficiente, voy a preparar la cocina. ¿Quieres ayudar?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1172
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_044b0240:

    # S "Okay, what do I do?"
    S "Vale, ¿qué hago?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1176
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1179
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_fe46fed0:

    # Ju "Thank you so much for staying with me today, [S]."
    Ju "Muchas gracias por quedarte hoy conmigo, [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1180
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_4bb53280:

    # Ju "I think it's getting late, maybe you should stay another night?"
    Ju "Creo que se está haciendo tarde, ¿quizás deberías quedarte otra noche?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1183
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_22151f54:

    # S "Now that you say that... you're right. I didn't notice the time passing."
    S "Ahora que lo dices... tienes razón. No me he dado cuenta del paso del tiempo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1186
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_c977ac76:

    # Ju "But you're sure that I'm not holding you back, right?"
    Ju "Pero estás segura de que no te retengo, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1187
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_343b4ba2:

    # Ju "If I was badgering you, then I'm sorry. I just really enjoy your company."
    Ju "Si te he dado la lata, lo siento. Es que me gusta mucho tu compañía."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1190
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_ae454705:

    # S "Me too, don't worry. It doesn't make a lot of difference whether I go today or tomorrow, really. I am on my own this time. I can decide how long I take."
    S "A mí también, no te preocupes. La verdad es que da igual que vaya hoy o mañana. Esta vez estoy sola. Puedo decidir cuánto tiempo me tomo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1193
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_83bb12e9:

    # Ju "I'm glad to hear that."
    Ju "Me alegro de oírlo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1196
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_3be5f0a5:

    # Ju "{i}*sigh*{/i} It really never changes out there. Nothing, and after that more nothing."
    Ju "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Realmente nunca cambia ahí fuera. Nada, y después más nada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1197
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_04cd75df:

    # Ju "The steppes are endless."
    Ju "Las estepas son interminables."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1200
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_ce087ac7:

    # Ju "Anyway, I think I will let you rest for now. Let's talk tomorrow again. Enjoy your sleep, [S]!"
    Ju "De todos modos, creo que te dejaré descansar por ahora. Hablaremos mañana de nuevo. ¡Disfruta de tu sueño, [S]!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1203
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_e977433a:

    # S "See you tomorrow!"
    S "Hasta mañana."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1206
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_29a2de66:

    # "She leaves..."
    "Ella se va..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1209
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_35859829:

    # St "Today felt so long, but I have not done a lot? We were outside in the backyard, prepared a dish..."
    St "El día de hoy ha parecido muy largo, pero no he hecho mucho... Estábamos fuera, en el patio trasero, preparando un plato..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1210
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_59822323:

    # St "Julia is so kind, and she has been around a lot. I feel like wanting to know more about her. Maybe I will get to know her partner as well?"
    St "Julia es muy amable, y ha pasado mucho por aquí. Tengo ganas de saber más sobre ella. ¿Quizás también pueda conocer a su pareja?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1213
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_34398d52:

    # St "The notes... they look like papers from a book. But they're handwritten."
    St "Las notas... parecen papeles de un libro. Pero están escritas a mano."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1214
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_a0d4fc4a:

    # "{i}\"May everything come true. May they believe. And may they laugh at their passions. For what they call passion is not really the energy of the soul, but merely friction between the soul and the outside world.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Que todo se haga realidad. Que crean. Y que se rían de sus pasiones. Porque lo que llaman pasión no es realmente la energía del alma, sino simplemente la fricción entre el alma y el mundo exterior.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1215
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_6b58a574:

    # "{i}\"But, above all, may they believe in themselves and become as helpless as children, because weakness is a great thing, and strength is nothing.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Pero, sobre todo, que crean en sí mismos y se vuelvan tan indefensos como los niños, porque la debilidad es una gran cosa, y la fuerza no es nada.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1216
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_0df6506b:

    # "{i}\"When we are born, we are soft and pliable. When we die, we are hard and insensitive. When a tree grows, it's tender and pliant. But when it's dry and hard, it dies.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Cuando nacemos, somos blandos y flexibles. Cuando morimos, somos duros e insensibles. Cuando un árbol crece, es tierno y flexible. Pero cuando se seca y se endurece, muere.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1217
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_e2daf4f2:

    # "{i}\"Hardness and strength are death's companions. Flexibility and softness are the embodiment of life. Because what has hardened will never win.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"La dureza y la fuerza son compañeras de la muerte. La flexibilidad y la suavidad son la encarnación de la vida. Porque lo que se ha endurecido nunca ganará.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1223
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_fd16ba28:

    # St "I wonder what the others are up to, right now. If [persistent.dad] knew where I am right now, I wonder what he would think."
    St "Me pregunto qué estarán haciendo los demás, en este momento. Si [persistent.dad] supiera dónde estoy ahora mismo, me pregunto qué pensaría."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1232
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_69f3481f:

    # "After a while..."
    "Después de un rato..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1235
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_eabb9359:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1241
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_a3fc443a:

    # S "{i}*yawn*"
    S "{i}*bostezo*"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1242
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_d8b5d5d2:

    # St "Another day in the zone..."
    St "Otro día en la zona..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1243
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_01256525:

    # St "...how many days has it been?"
    St "... ¿cuántos días han pasado?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1246
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_eb1ada00:

    # Ju "Good morning! Are you ready for breakfast? Have a seat."
    Ju "¡Buenos días! ¿Estás preparada para desayunar? Siéntate."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1249
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_0680c15a:

    # S "Heh, did I? Good morning..."
    S "¿Ah, sí? Buenos días..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1252
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_c361f2a7:

    # Ju "Hey, look... I know you've stayed here for more than I can ask of you."
    Ju "Ey, mira... Sé que te has quedado aquí más de lo que puedo pedirte."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1253
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_9eec8e15:

    # Ju "But I thought about yesterday, and it made me wonder about some things about you."
    Ju "Pero he pensado en lo de ayer, y me ha hecho preguntarme algunas cosas sobre ti."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1256
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_19800daa:

    # Ju "Do you mind if we sit under the tree today, at least for a bit?"
    Ju "¿Te importa que nos sentemos hoy bajo el árbol, al menos un rato?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1257
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_b3a2999b:

    # Ju "We could have some fruit, and talk some more. I promise that this time I will listen instead of talking your ears off. I am curious about you."
    Ju "Podríamos comer algo de fruta y hablar un poco más. Te prometo que esta vez te escucharé en lugar de hablarte hasta la saciedad. Siento curiosidad por ti."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1258
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_25f1a3e2:

    # Ju "I still know very little about you, and the things you do, and the shadow of the tree is such a nice place to have engaging conversations."
    Ju "Todavía sé muy poco sobre ti y las cosas que haces, y la sombra del árbol es un lugar muy agradable para mantener conversaciones interesantes."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1259
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_b57b533c:

    # Ju "So, will you stay another little while? Then you can be on your way."
    Ju "Entonces, ¿te quedarás otro ratito? Entonces podrás seguir tu camino."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1264
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_77ccf39b:

    # S "I'd like to, yes. My time here has been so peaceful, when I expected nothing but danger and violence."
    S "Me gustaría, sí. El tiempo que he pasado aquí ha sido muy tranquilo, cuando no esperaba más que peligro y violencia."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1267
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_e8844151:

    # Ju "Amazing. I'll see you outside then!"
    Ju "Es increíble. ¡Te veré fuera entonces!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1274
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_07396f33:

    # S "I really enjoyed the time here, [Ju]. But I think it's time that I leave. My time with you was great, but I do have people who are waiting for me."
    S "He disfrutado mucho el tiempo aquí, [Ju]. Pero creo que es hora de que me vaya. El tiempo que pasé contigo fue estupendo, pero tengo gente que me espera."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1277
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_c2c0ad64:

    # Ju "It's okay. It was great as it lasted."
    Ju "No pasa nada. Fue genial mientras duró."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1280
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_5d8b7a73:

    # Ju "I really mean it. Thank you for yesterday."
    Ju "Lo digo en serio. Gracias por lo de ayer."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1281
translate spanish d11b_stay_1_ead31ef7:

    # Ju "Let me know when you finished your meal. I will prepare everything for your departure, [S]."
    Ju "Avísame cuando hayas terminado de comer. Prepararé todo para tu partida, [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1289
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1292
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_eee406f5:

    # Ju "Hey, [S], come here, you can lean against the grass, see?"
    Ju "Ey, [S], ven aquí, puedes apoyarte en la hierba, ¿lo ves?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1293
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_cca9b1c7:

    # S "{i}*laughs*{/i} Are you sure that's grass? Those look more like bushes!"
    S "{i}*risas*{/i} ¿Estás segura de que eso es hierba? ¡Parecen más bien arbustos!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1294
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_c96c8d8d:

    # Ju "It's not as hard as it looks."
    Ju "No es tan dura como parece."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1297
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_50982712:

    # Ju "Can I ask you something?"
    Ju "¿Puedo preguntarte algo?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1298
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_18981dd1:

    # S "Sure... I mean, it depends on the question?"
    S "Claro... Depende de la pregunta..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1299
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_a9fb7897:

    # Ju "Is there anything that you always wanted to do but never had a chance to?"
    Ju "¿Hay algo que siempre hayas querido hacer pero que nunca hayas podido?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1300
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_58afa3c8:

    # S "As in..."
    S "Como..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1301
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_d3f59467:

    # Ju "Anything."
    Ju "Cualquier cosa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1302
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1305
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_8b82e232:

    # Ju "You look like you're very driven, but maybe if you allowed yourself to pause for a second, you might dream up something different for yourself."
    Ju "Te ves muy impulsada, pero tal vez si te permitieras hacer una pausa por un segundo, podrías soñar con algo diferente para ti."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1306
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_739d7814:

    # Ju "I'm sure there is something that you never had the opportunity to do, but you wished you had? Could be, I don't know... eat certain food, or be a certain someone, or..."
    Ju "Seguro que hay algo que nunca has tenido la oportunidad de hacer, pero que desearías haber hecho. Podría ser, no sé... comer cierta comida, o ser cierta persona, o..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1309
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_619db71a:

    # S "I think... you know... {i}*sigh*{/i} it's silly."
    S "Creo que... ya sabes... {i}*suspiro*{/i} es una tontería."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1312
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_002450f6:

    # Ju "You can tell me. I can guarantee you it's not."
    Ju "Puedes decírmelo. Puedo garantizarte que no es así."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1315
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_9f3df93a:

    # S "I've read about the open sea, the vaste dunes made of salt water, and the boats that ride the dunes. I wonder how it would feel like, to ride the dunes, the waves, on one of those big boats."
    S "He leído sobre el mar abierto, las vastas dunas de agua salada y las embarcaciones que recorren las dunas. Me pregunto qué se sentiría al cabalgar las dunas, las olas, en uno de esos grandes barcos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1316
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_2dd2bbb3:

    # S "In the story, it seems like a grand adventure, the way they blow a horn when they take off..."
    S "En la historia, parece una gran aventura, la forma en que tocan la campana cuando salen..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1319
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_8f88992d:

    # S "I told you it's silly, but..."
    S "Te he dicho que es una tontería, pero..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1322
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_8f5c0515:

    # Ju "That's not silly at all! It's not silly to have these goals."
    Ju "¡No es ninguna tontería! No es una tontería tener esos objetivos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1325
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_85c65561:

    # S "I don't know... I don't want to assume anything, but... it does seem that people forget how things once were. You know?"
    S "No sé... No quiero suponer nada, pero... parece que la gente se olvida de cómo eran las cosas antes. ¿Sabes?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1326
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_b99c4a74:

    # S "The things that were possible and we had the means to do... even if there is a... giant city in front of them, that reminds them of some of those things!"
    S "Las cosas que eran posibles y teníamos los medios para hacer... ¡Aunque haya una... ciudad gigante delante de ellos, que les recuerde algunas de esas cosas!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1329
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_1539c476:

    # Ju "They may be too caught up in daily struggles. Or they waited for too long, and let the moment pass them by."
    Ju "Puede que estén demasiado atrapados en las luchas diarias. O han esperado demasiado tiempo y han dejado pasar el momento."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1330
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_f881fd26:

    # S "You look sad, [Ju]. Are you worrying about Kirill?"
    S "Pareces triste, [Ju]. ¿Estás preocupada por Kirill?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1333
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_27c461d5:

    # Ju "{i}*sigh*{/i} I don't know, [S]. To be honest, he has been out for so long, I stopped counting the days."
    Ju "{i}*suspiro*{/i} No sé, [S]. Para ser sincera, lleva tanto tiempo fuera que he dejado de contar los días."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1336
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_4302ca7c:

    # Ju "At this point, I don't know if he will return! And I keep waiting and waiting. But what if there is nothing to wait for, and we can never continue our journey?"
    Ju "En este momento, ¡no sé si volverá! Y sigo esperando y esperando. Pero, ¿y si no hay nada que esperar y no podemos continuar nuestro viaje?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1339
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_c6faa3f6:

    # Ju "It has been so long since I saw someone else, and I am so happy to see you here. But what if all this waiting was in vain? What if he is no longer there?"
    Ju "Ha pasado tanto tiempo desde que vi a alguien más, y estoy tan feliz de verte aquí. Pero, ¿y si toda esta espera ha sido en vano? ¿Y si ya no está ahí?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1342
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_7e205347:

    # S "We can go out there and look for him together?"
    S "¿Podemos salir a buscarlo juntas?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1343
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_5dc903a8:

    # S "I know it's rough out there, but we can get you out of here."
    S "Sé que es duro ahí fuera, pero podemos sacarte de aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1344
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_47ab14de:

    # S "You will be too lonely out here, [Ju]. Let's leave this place together?"
    S "Te sentirás demasiado sola aquí fuera, [Ju]. ¿Dejemos este lugar juntas?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1347
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_1c3490f3:

    # Ju "No..."
    Ju "No..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1348
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_8da2954a:

    # "She wipes her tears away..."
    "Ella se limpia las lágrimas..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1349
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_9a8fd5ac:

    # Ju "I'm sorry, I don't know what overcame me."
    Ju "Lo siento, no sé qué me ha superado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1352
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_b0191f04:

    # Ju "I promised to wait for him, and I want to do so."
    Ju "Prometí esperarle y quiero hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1353
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_be9fe76c:

    # Ju "I know that there is a chance that he won't come, but now is not yet the time to move on."
    Ju "Sé que existe la posibilidad de que no venga, pero aún no es el momento de seguir adelante."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1356
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_22cde896:

    # Ju "Come, [S], let's go inside to your bedroom. I want to show you something."
    Ju "Ven, [S], vamos dentro a tu habitación. Quiero enseñarte algo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1357
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_5b510e3d:

    # S "Is it the books?"
    S "¿Son los libros?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1358
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_d270b6d4:

    # Ju "No... something better."
    Ju "No... algo mejor."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1361
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_d85ff20e:

    # S "What is it? It looks so pretty."
    S "¿Qué es? Parece tan bonito."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1362
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_0dffb669:

    # Ju "Inside this... lies Kirill's gift to me."
    Ju "Dentro de esto... se encuentra el regalo de Kirills para mí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1363
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_9151ed56:

    # Ju "He gave it to me when he proposed."
    Ju "Me lo regaló cuando me propuso matrimonio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1364
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_7ae2db13:

    # S "No way, he did? I'm so happy for you!"
    S "No puede ser, ¿lo hizo? ¡Me alegro mucho por ti!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1365
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_2f8ea9c8:

    # S "Can I see it?"
    S "¿Puedo verlo?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1368
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_baf033c3:

    # Ju "Sorry, [S]. I really like you, but this one is just between us. I'm keeping it in here, safe. It's for our eyes only, and when he returns, I will wear it!"
    Ju "Lo siento, [S]. Me gustas mucho, pero eso queda entre nosotros. Lo mantengo aquí, a salvo. Es sólo para nuestros ojos, y cuando vuelva, ¡lo usaré!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1369
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_9bb7d88d:

    # S "And this is why you're staying..."
    S "Y por eso te quedas..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1372
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_b2a8a65d:

    # Ju "Yeah. Even though... I don't know how long it takes, or even if he comes back..."
    Ju "Sí. Aunque... No sé cuánto tiempo tardará, o incluso si volverá..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1373
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_8f563cbb:

    # Ju "But this keeps me going, you know?"
    Ju "Pero esto me hace seguir adelante, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1374
translate spanish d11b_stay_2_eba78702:

    # S "I understand."
    S "Lo comprendo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1380
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_33013df1:

    # Ju "Say... do you also feel so tired, [S]?"
    Ju "Dime... ¿también te sientes tan cansada, [S]?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1381
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_e0a0ccd4:

    # S "I do. It feels like it has been a long time since I slept."
    S "Lo hago. Parece que hace mucho tiempo que no duermo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1382
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_521ccb4f:

    # Ju "Do you want to stay by my side? You could sleep here again, for... longer... this time. I think... I need the rest."
    Ju "¿Quieres quedarte a mi lado? Podrías volver a dormir aquí, durante... más tiempo... esta vez. Creo que... necesito descansar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1387
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_8602b1c2:

    # S "I'm sorry, [Ju]. But I think it's really time for me to get back on track."
    S "Lo siento, [Ju]. Pero creo que ya es hora de que vuelva a la carga."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1388
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_08e54b99:

    # Ju "..."
    Ju "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1389
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_c896522c:

    # Ju "I know."
    Ju "Lo sé."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1392
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_cbdd60b1:

    # "Eventually..."
    "Finalmente..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1396
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_64529910:

    # S "I think we could... maybe he will show up tomorrow?"
    S "Creo que podríamos... ¿Tal vez aparezca mañana?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1397
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_6cb26002:

    # Ju "Maybe. And if he doesn't, I will wait another day."
    Ju "Tal vez. Y si no lo hace, esperaré otro día."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1400
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_af53fea1:

    # "As she says so, she stares in the distance for a few seconds, then gives a faint smile that doesn't hide her true feelings."
    "Mientras ella lo dice, se queda mirando a lo lejos durante unos segundos, y luego esboza una leve sonrisa que no oculta sus verdaderos sentimientos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1401
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_344fd68a:

    # "She then bids a good night and goes to her room."
    "A continuación, le da las buenas noches y ella se va a su habitación."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1402
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_347bdcab:

    # "The next day is greeted again by Julia, who once more serves breakfast."
    "Al día siguiente eres recibida de nuevo por Julia, que vuelve a servirte el desayuno."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1403
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_d204686a:

    # "During breakfast, Julia places a hand atop some of the books Kirill has left behind, and starts telling the story of some of their voyages together; the people they met, the places they saw..."
    "Durante el desayuno, Julia coloca una mano encima de algunos de los libros que Kirill ha dejado, y empieza a contar la historia de algunos de sus viajes juntos; la gente que conocieron, los lugares que vieron..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1404
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_87b01d97:

    # "Time flies and again, there's once again an opportunity for a little picnic under the shadow of the tree. The stories continue, painting a tapestry of vivid colours."
    "El tiempo vuela y, de nuevo, se presenta la oportunidad de hacer un pequeño picnic a la sombra del árbol. Las historias continúan, pintando un tapiz de colores vivos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1407
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_4730381f:

    # "As the hours grow late, so the storytelling changes, moving from more personal detailed events, to a larger scale."
    "A medida que las horas se hacen tarde, la narración cambia, pasando de los acontecimientos más personales y detallados a una escala mayor."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1408
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_43fd3247:

    # "From the story of Julia and Kirill, the story grows into the retelling of a far gone time..."
    "A partir de la historia de Julia y Kirill, el relato se convierte en la narración de un tiempo lejano..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1409
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_bfb4a365:

    # "...describing global events and a world of grand proportions, dominated by advanced technology and sciences now lost to the sands of time."
    "... describiendo acontecimientos globales y un mundo de grandes proporciones, dominado por la tecnología avanzada y las ciencias ahora perdidas en las arenas del tiempo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1412
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_17195a34:

    # "With each new story told, the world around seems to come to a standstill, and all the time passed now seems like a mere afterthought."
    "Con cada nueva historia que se cuenta, el mundo que le rodea parece detenerse, y todo el tiempo transcurrido parece ahora una mera ocurrencia."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1413
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_e922ecdb:

    # "As the leaves start falling off the tree, two figures sit together, sharing moments of learning from one another, genuine connection, laughter, sadness and the simple joy of companionship and peace."
    "Cuando las hojas empiezan a caer del árbol, dos figuras se sientan juntas, compartiendo momentos de aprendizaje mutuo, de auténtica conexión, de risas, de tristeza y de la simple alegría del compañerismo y la paz."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1421
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_88eb2ff5:

    # "A lot of time goes by, and so does the need to explore and continue along the path. The world that once was, is now as present as ever."
    "Pasa mucho tiempo, y también la necesidad de explorar y continuar el camino. El mundo que una vez fue, está ahora tan presente como siempre."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1422
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_c5c018f7:

    # "Life in the distance does not seem to matter anymore. Memories of the past become blurred, until the past and the present blend together..."
    "La vida en la distancia ya no parece importar. Los recuerdos del pasado se difuminan, hasta que el pasado y el presente se mezclan..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1423
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_8e7595e8:

    # "...fading into the embrace of an eternal rest."
    "... desvaneciéndose en el abrazo de un descanso eterno."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1427
translate spanish d11b_stay_end_5202cc5a:

    # "[S] never returned home."
    "[S] nunca volvió a casa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1442
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_72cd1679:

    # Ju "I hope you will find what you're looking for, [S]."
    Ju "Espero que encuentres lo que buscas, [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1444
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_f4847cd1:

    # S "Thank you for letting me stay. I will not forget your kindness."
    S "Gracias por permitirme quedarme. No olvidaré tu amabilidad."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1445
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_7357dc2b:

    # Ju "I am glad to have met you. I was happy to see someone else come by after so long."
    Ju "Me alegro de haberte conocido. Me alegra ver que alguien más ha venido después de tanto tiempo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1448
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_abb05b9f:

    # Ju "Take care out there, [S], okay?"
    Ju "Ten cuidado ahí fuera, [S], ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1449
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_9abc50a7:

    # Ju "Goodbye, [S]."
    Ju "Adiós, [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1452
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_9a734ca6:

    # S "I will. Goodbye, [Ju]."
    S "Lo haré. Adiós, [Ju]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1457
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_c52856c6:

    # S "Thank you for letting me stay. And for everything you showed me."
    S "Gracias por permitirme quedarme. Y por todo lo que me has enseñado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1458
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_e84050ee:

    # S "I won't forget you."
    S "No te olvidaré."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1461
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_ea4e1b1e:

    # S "I hope you will see him again soon. And that you will stay as kind as you are."
    S "Espero que vuelvas a verlo pronto. Y que sigas siendo tan amable como lo eres."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1464
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_ed5b317d:

    # Ju "I will, [S]. I am sure of it."
    Ju "Lo haré, [S]. Estoy seguro de ello."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1467
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_785379c7:

    # Ju "And you pursue everything you want, okay?"
    Ju "Y persigues todo lo que quieres, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1468
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_31d2ec5d:

    # Ju "Even if I don't know what it is, but there must be something."
    Ju "Aunque no sepa lo que es, debe haber algo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1471
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_a0da8ce9:

    # Ju "You never know... when you will stop having the chance."
    Ju "Nunca sabes... cuándo dejarás de tener la oportunidad."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1474
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_3b324295:

    # Ju "Goodbye, [S]. Farewell."
    Ju "Adiós, [S]. Adiós."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1477
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_c2151f41:

    # S "Farewell, [Ju]."
    S "Adiós, [Ju]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1482
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_c52856c6_1:

    # S "Thank you for letting me stay. And for everything you showed me."
    S "Gracias por permitirme quedarme. Y por todo lo que me has enseñado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1483
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_e84050ee_1:

    # S "I won't forget you."
    S "No te olvidaré."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1486
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_e1bffbb7:

    # S "And [Ju]... you can not wait forever. Please remember that."
    S "Y [Ju]... No puedes esperar eternamente. Por favor, recuérdalo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1487
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_aea2ea7e:

    # S "Some day you have to get out of here. There is a chance he won't come back."
    S "Algún día tendrás que salir de aquí. Existe la posibilidad de que él no vuelva."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1490
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_0e4257e9:

    # Ju "I know, [S]... I think I know that... I have to let go."
    Ju "Lo sé, [S]... Creo que lo sé... Tengo que dejarlo ir."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1493
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_8d2dda51:

    # Ju "But you, don't stop dreaming, okay?"
    Ju "Pero tú, no dejes de soñar, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1494
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_4e8e0136:

    # Ju "And keep looking for places. Travel around and explore as much as you can."
    Ju "Y sigue buscando lugares. Viaja y explora todo lo que puedas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1495
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_6395ed02:

    # Ju "You never know when you will stop having the chance, like me."
    Ju "Nunca sabes cuándo dejarás de tener la oportunidad, como yo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1496
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_3b324295_1:

    # Ju "Goodbye, [S]. Farewell."
    Ju "Adiós, [S]. Adiós."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1499
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_f04fcf51:

    # Ju "I will miss you very much."
    Ju "Te echaré mucho de menos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1502
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_c2151f41_1:

    # S "Farewell, [Ju]."
    S "Adiós, [Ju]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1503
translate spanish d11b_julia_endings_bbe75ce4:

    # S "I will miss you too."
    S "Yo también te echaré de menos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1531
translate spanish d11b93_2bafc2a4:

    # St "Julia... wha-... the tree is dead. The house..."
    St "Julia... ¿qué?... el árbol está muerto. La casa..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1532
translate spanish d11b93_1f96f513:

    # "Realisation dawns that this may well have been a mortal trap."
    "Te das cuenta de que esto podría haber sido una trampa mortal."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1533
translate spanish d11b93_e7de21d1:

    # "How long was she in this place for? Was it a hallucination?"
    "¿Cuánto tiempo permaneció en ese lugar? ¿Fue una alucinación?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1536
translate spanish d11b93_2966b3d4:

    # St "Gods above, what have I done? How much time did I lose?"
    St "Dioses, ¿qué he hecho? ¿Cuánto tiempo he perdido?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1539
translate spanish d11b93_75d4520e:

    # St "What happened to me, really?"
    St "¿Qué me ha pasado, de verdad?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1548
translate spanish d11b93_2bafc2a4_1:

    # St "Julia... wha-... the tree is dead. The house..."
    St "Julia... ¿qué?... el árbol está muerto. La casa..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1549
translate spanish d11b93_1f96f513_1:

    # "Realisation dawns that this may well have been a mortal trap."
    "Te das cuenta de que esto podría haber sido una trampa mortal."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1550
translate spanish d11b93_e7de21d1_1:

    # "How long was she in this place for? Was it a hallucination?"
    "¿Cuánto tiempo permaneció en ese lugar? ¿Fue una alucinación?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1553
translate spanish d11b93_2966b3d4_1:

    # St "Gods above, what have I done? How much time did I lose?"
    St "Dioses, ¿qué he hecho? ¿Cuánto tiempo he perdido?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1554
translate spanish d11b93_75d4520e_1:

    # St "What happened to me, really?"
    St "¿Qué me ha pasado, de verdad?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1557
translate spanish d11b93_fa350079:

    # St "It seemed so... real..."
    St "Parecía tan... real..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1558
translate spanish d11b93_cfd01b59:

    # St "Maybe [persistent.dad] was right, back then..."
    St "Quizá [persistent.dad] tenía razón, en aquel entonces..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1561
translate spanish d11b93_2ac610d8:

    # Z "{i}...but some things in this world follow their own logic.{/i}"
    Z "{i}... pero algunas cosas en este mundo siguen su propia lógica.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1562
translate spanish d11b93_f2259977:

    # Z "{i}And it is better for us not to question everything.{/i}"
    Z "{i}Y es mejor para nosotros no cuestionar todo.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1565
translate spanish d11b93_201a8c35:

    # St "I can almost hear him say it, and I think I get what he was saying, now."
    St "Casi puedo oírle deciéndomelo, y creo que ahora entiendo lo que estaba hablando."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1566
translate spanish d11b93_dbd11d00:

    # St "Still..."
    St "Aún así..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1569
translate spanish d11b93_d824d4e2:

    # St "Julia... I hope she was able to let go."
    St "Julia... Espero que ella pudiera liberarse."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1583
translate spanish d11b103anim_b6680fda:

    # "Some time later, closer to the factory..."
    "Algún tiempo después, más cerca de la fábrica..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1589
translate spanish d11b103anim_ab61e4ca:

    # "On the way to the factory, bursts of red light illuminate the sky, contouring the place."
    "De camino a la fábrica, ráfagas de luz roja iluminan el cielo, contorneando el lugar."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1590
translate spanish d11b103anim_b5fc1c3e:

    # St "That must be one of the anomalies I've read about. Although I am still far away, I can already feel the heat that emanates from there."
    St "Debe ser una de las anomalías sobre las que he leído. Aunque todavía estoy lejos, ya puedo sentir el calor que emana de allí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1594
translate spanish d11b103anim_fdcd3b64:

    # St "The factory is close. And so is the dust."
    St "La fábrica está cerca. Y también el polvo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1595
translate spanish d11b103anim_6b573946:

    # St "I will need my mask in there."
    St "Necesitaré mi máscara ahí dentro."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1598
translate spanish d11b103anim_bd17e1b5:

    # "A huge complex of structures stretches ahead. The old factory buildings are tall, and sunlight barely pierces through them."
    "Un enorme complejo de estructuras se extiende por delante. Los viejos edificios de la fábrica son altos, y la luz del sol apenas los atraviesa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1599
translate spanish d11b103anim_b03528ef:

    # "The remains of the age of industrialisation and progress stand abandoned to the ravages of time, yet endure, after a fashion."
    "Los restos de la era de la industrialización y el progreso se encuentran abandonados a los estragos del tiempo, pero perduran, en cierto modo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1600
translate spanish d11b103anim_f8c46940:

    # "Brown dust fills the air, as one thought surfaces: where to start?"
    "El polvo marrón llena el aire, mientras un pensamiento aflora: ¿Por dónde empezar?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1603
translate spanish d11b103anim_906d4a66:

    # St "\"You will know what you're looking for when you see it.\""
    St "\"Sabrás lo que buscas cuando lo veas.\""

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1604
translate spanish d11b103anim_5a1811b4:

    # St "I hope I won't get any unwanted surprises as I'm looking for it."
    St "Espero no llevarme ninguna sorpresa no deseada mientras lo busco."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1607
translate spanish d11b103anim_4399a845:

    # St "I should find a way into this complex..."
    St "Debería encontrar una forma de entrar en este complejo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1610
translate spanish d11b103anim_c7059e93:

    # "Stepping inside, metal structures pave the way. Dead silence is the only thing greeting the sound of the steps of the new visitor. An industrial graveyard."
    "Al entrar, las estructuras metálicas allanan el camino. El silencio sepulcral es lo único que saluda al sonido de los pasos del nuevo visitante. Un cementerio industrial."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1613
translate spanish d11b103anim_4a8282d3:

    # St "How can something this tall be buried by sand?"
    St "¿Cómo es posible que algo tan alto esté enterrado por la arena?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1616
translate spanish d11b103anim_4db4ab44:

    # St "Or maybe... just most of it?"
    St "O quizás... ¿Sólo la mayor parte?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1617
translate spanish d11b103anim_baea6f15:

    # St "Either way, I should try to be as quiet and discrete as possible, just in case."
    St "En cualquier caso, debería intentar ser lo más silenciosa y discreta posible, por si acaso."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1624
translate spanish d11b103anim_8b650b54:

    # "Light barely shines through. The Zone's clouds are thick and gloomy, but at least the factory roof has enough gaps in it to allow for some visibility."
    "La luz apenas brilla. Las nubes de la Zona son densas y sombrías, pero al menos el techo de la fábrica tiene suficientes huecos para permitir algo de visibilidad."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1625
translate spanish d11b103anim_25b05342:

    # S "{i}*sigh*"
    S "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1626
translate spanish d11b103anim_3b891e59:

    # St "I can see the other buildings from here... this might take an entire day to explore."
    St "Puedo ver los otros edificios desde aquí... Esto podría llevarme un día entero de exploración."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1629
translate spanish d11b103anim_19e94753:

    # "Looking down..."
    "Mirando hacia abajo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1630
translate spanish d11b103anim_fd548951:

    # St "Are those...?"
    St "¿Seran esos...?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1633
translate spanish d11b103anim_2628dc5d:

    # St "I should climb down and take a look."
    St "Debería bajar y echar un vistazo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1640
translate spanish d11b103anim_eabb9359:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1643
translate spanish d11b103anim_f7cfa931:

    # St "It seems that at least I am the only living being in here."
    St "Parece que al menos yo soy el único ser vivo aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1644
translate spanish d11b103anim_028bb3be:

    # St "So many bones... the dust mixes with the sand, I can barely tell what I'm stepping into."
    St "Tantos huesos... El polvo se mezcla con la arena, apenas puedo distinguir lo que estoy pisando."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1647
translate spanish d11b103anim_6e1d12d7:

    # St "But why are they all stacked up here?"
    St "Pero, ¿por qué están todos amontonados aquí?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1650
translate spanish d11b103anim_eabb9359_1:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1651
translate spanish d11b103anim_5323733e:

    # St "Is that... some kind of board?"
    St "¿Es eso... algún tipo de pizarra?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1654
translate spanish d11b103anim_e3ee330d:

    # "The tail end of a written text is barely noticeable on the corner of a whiteboard, hanging on a section of wall that is covered in debris. After shoving it out of the way, it appears that the debris actually has protected the writing."
    "La cola de un texto escrito apenas se percibe en la esquina de una pizarra, colgada en una parte de la pared cubierta de escombros. Después de apartarla, parece que los escombros han protegido realmente el escrito."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1655
translate spanish d11b103anim_d59fb2c9:

    # "{i}\"Duty roster: Team 1, 3 and 7 on guard duty rotations, shift changes at 0600, 1400 and 2200.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Lista de turnos: Equipo 1, 3 y 7 en turnos de guardia, cambios de turno a las 06:00, 14:00 y 22:00.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1657
translate spanish d11b103anim_11e5e9ba:

    # "{i}\"Team 2, maintenance duty upper levels, remember to double check the ventilation shafts. I suspect birds are trying to nest in them again. Do NOT let the machines overheat again.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Equipo 2, servicio de mantenimiento en los niveles superiores, recordad comprobar los conductos de ventilación. Sospecho que los pájaros están intentando anidar en ellos de nuevo. NO dejéis que las máquinas se vuelvan a sobrecalentar.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1659
translate spanish d11b103anim_a704da18:

    # "{i}\"Team 4 maintenance ground level. Routine monthly checks have shown a few malfunctions in the lower pumps. I want a status report as soon as you have found the cause. The exact specifics are posted in the crew room whiteboard.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Equipo 4 de mantenimiento a nivel del suelo. Las comprobaciones mensuales de rutina han mostrado algunas averías en las bombas inferiores. Quiero un informe de situación en cuanto hayáis encontrado la causa. Los detalles exactos están publicados en la pizarra de la sala de la cuadrilla.{/i}\""

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1661
translate spanish d11b103anim_d46086d1:

    # "{i}\"Note to shift manager 3: team 5 and 6 are on special duty in the basement level.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Nota para el jefe de turno 3: los equipos 5 y 6 están de guardia especial en el nivel del sótano.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1662
translate spanish d11b103anim_89519b51:

    # "{i}\"Remember that there is to be no shift exchanges outside these two teams, because they are the only ones with clearance to the basement level.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Recuerda que no debe haber intercambios de turno fuera de estos dos equipos, porque son los únicos con acceso al nivel del sótano.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1663
translate spanish d11b103anim_12063f61:

    # "{i}\"I do not want another fuckup. We do not want to terminate another employee for having swapped a shift.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"No quiero otra cagada. No queremos despedir a otro empleado por haber intercambiado un turno.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1664
translate spanish d11b103anim_ea43c165:

    # St "I have no idea what most of this means. The only clear thing is that if they didn't want just anybody in the basement, it had to be an important place."
    St "No tengo ni idea de lo que significa la mayor parte de esto. Lo único claro es que si no querían a cualquiera en el sótano, tenía que ser un lugar importante."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1670
translate spanish d11b118_c53271c6:

    # "Following a small corridor that leads downstairs, the path leads to what looks like the entrance to a basement..."
    "Siguiendo un pequeño pasillo que conduce a la planta baja, el camino lleva a lo que parece la entrada de un sótano..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1673
translate spanish d11b118_d07aee89:

    # St "One more dead body. Sorry to disturb your peace, friend..."
    St "Otro cadáver más. Siento perturbar tu paz, amigo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1674
translate spanish d11b118_83148d90:

    # St "This leads all the way down, doesn't it..."
    St "Esto lleva todo el camino hacia abajo, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1677
translate spanish d11b118_06a6cdd9:

    # St "Yep... and I can't see a thing."
    St "Sí... y no puedo ver nada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1678
translate spanish d11b118_a384de7f:

    # St "My eyes start hurting. It's probably the smog."
    St "Me empiezan a doler los ojos. Probablemente sea la niebla tóxica."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1681
translate spanish d11b118_a581d976:

    # St "My goggles should help."
    St "Mis gafas deberían ayudarme."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1685
translate spanish d11b118_a8c5b37b:

    # St "Okay... here goes nothing."
    St "Vale... aquí no hay nada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1693
translate spanish d11b118_7b55edd4:

    # "To the side of the remains of this individual, lies a mostly ruined binder. Gently prying open the hard cover reveals a few pages of calculations and, at the bottom, barely legible, a hastily scribbled bit of text."
    "A un lado de los restos de este individuo, se encuentra una carpeta casi arruinada. Al abrir con cuidado la tapa dura, aparecen unas cuantas páginas de cálculos y, en la parte inferior, apenas legible, un texto garabateado a toda prisa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1694
translate spanish d11b118_8846e662:

    # St "There is a note..."
    St "Hay una nota..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1695
translate spanish d11b118_27ddd854:

    # "{i}\"We thought this was just a regular bombing, but they have been relentless and we have had to seal the basement to save the projects running here. I had to hear the screams of my colleagues dying behind the entrance.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Pensábamos que se trataba de un bombardeo normal, pero han sido implacables y hemos tenido que sellar el sótano para salvar los proyectos que funcionan aquí. He tenido que oír los gritos de mis compañeros muriendo detrás de la entrada.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1696
translate spanish d11b118_52f135f3:

    # "{i}\"And now the extractor fans have stopped working. Soon the gasses will saturate this entire level. How do I tell my colleagues we are going to die? If anybody should read this, know that I did my duty, and that my soul is doomed for it.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Y ahora los extractores han dejado de funcionar. Pronto los gases saturarán todo este nivel. ¿Cómo les digo a mis compañeros que vamos a morir? Si alguien lee esto, que sepa que he cumplido con mi deber y que mi alma está condenada por ello.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1697
translate spanish d11b118_bb3475d6:

    # St "Poor people. They died down here, trapped like rats. I hope my mask holds up, and that whatever gas they were writing about has evaporated over the years."
    St "Pobre gente. Han muerto aquí abajo, atrapados como ratas. Espero que mi máscara aguante, y que el gas que escribían se haya evaporado con los años."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1698
translate spanish d11b118_ad14d115:

    # St "I wonder if [persistent.dad] also encounters testimony of the End of Days, when he explores places such as this. It's kind of an odd feeling."
    St "Me pregunto si [persistent.dad] también encuentra testimonios del Fin de los Días, cuando explora lugares como éste. Es una sensación extraña."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1704
translate spanish d11b121_b8586961:

    # St "At least the building seems stable."
    St "Al menos el edificio parece estable."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1705
translate spanish d11b121_fd3e6c75:

    # St "I need to be careful though. I don't want to be trapped in this oversized coffin."
    St "Sin embargo, tengo que tener cuidado. No quiero quedarme atrapada en este ataúd de gran tamaño."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1712
translate spanish d11b121_d048436a:

    # St "I still can't see where this leads, but at least I can tell what's around me."
    St "Todavía no puedo ver a dónde conduce esto, pero al menos puedo saber qué hay a mi alrededor."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1715
translate spanish d11b121_361f37e3:

    # St "Now... where to next..."
    St "Ahora... hacia dónde..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1716
translate spanish d11b121_c88a7367:

    # St "No way down here."
    St "No hay manera de bajar aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1719
translate spanish d11b121_eabb9359:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1720
translate spanish d11b121_36396707:

    # St "Is that ladder the only way down?"
    St "¿Es esa escalera la única forma de bajar?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1721
translate spanish d11b121_8609ad6f:

    # St "I have to try..."
    St "Lo tengo que intentar..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1725
translate spanish d11b121_3227a5b3:

    # "Climbing down the old ladder isn't easy, but manageable."
    "Bajar la vieja escalera no es fácil, pero sí manejable."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1726
translate spanish d11b121_1d07ad0f:

    # St "There must've been another way before..."
    St "Antes debía haber otra manera..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1732
translate spanish d11b121_eabb9359_1:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1733
translate spanish d11b121_e537e253:

    # St "Where does it end..."
    St "¿Dónde termina...?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1743
translate spanish d11b121_39b5ca03:

    # St "More corpses. I wonder how they came to an end; what were their final moments like?"
    St "Más cadáveres. Me pregunto cómo llegaron a su fin; cómo fueron sus últimos momentos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1746
translate spanish d11b121_e305f9d0:

    # St "They're everywhere. So many."
    St "Están por todas partes. Son tantos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1754
translate spanish d11b121_16584967:

    # St "Once again, one of these binders seems to have preserved a bit of text."
    St "Una vez más, una de estas carpetas parece haber conservado un poco de texto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1757
translate spanish d11b121_9b1a8411:

    # "{i}\"Transportation manifesto: 2 replacement valves for hydraulic press nr 14.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Manifiesto de transporte: 2 válvulas de recambio para la prensa hidráulica nº 14.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1758
translate spanish d11b121_02d2ead1:

    # "{i}\"3 new generator units for the outer perimeter surveillance system. 1 case of Shiraz for the director's office.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"3 nuevas unidades generadoras para el sistema de vigilancia del perímetro exterior. 1 caja de Shiraz para el despacho del director.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1759
translate spanish d11b121_16db3d1b:

    # "{i}\"1 Box nr 304087, to be retrieved from the Basement Vault.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"1 Caja nº 304087, a recuperar de la Bóveda del Sótano.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1760
translate spanish d11b121_790cfe2f:

    # "{i}\"Note: only team 5 should handle the last item. Any individual involved in handling it must be logged and identity checked.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Nota: sólo el equipo 5 debe manipular el último objeto. Cualquier persona que intervenga en su manipulación debe ser registrada y su identidad comprobada.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1761
translate spanish d11b121_6874cf30:

    # "{i}\"Violation of the security procedures will be prosecuted to the fullest extent.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"La violación de los procedimientos de seguridad se perseguirá con todo su rigor.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1762
translate spanish d11b121_e514aa7d:

    # "{i}\"45 boxes of screws nr 23. 15 new solar panels.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"45 cajas de tornillos nº 23. 15 paneles solares nuevos.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1763
translate spanish d11b121_57b959c8:

    # St "What's a Shiraz? And what was so important in Box 304087?"
    St "¿Qué es un Shiraz? ¿Y qué era tan importante en la caja 304087?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1769
translate spanish d11b130_88f080d2:

    # St "I want to find out what's at the bottom of this."
    St "Quiero averiguar qué hay en el fondo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1770
translate spanish d11b130_062044b7:

    # St "I hope I didn't come here in vain."
    St "Espero no haber venido en vano."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1773
translate spanish d11b130_9d8caa80:

    # "Stepping downstairs, the skeleton right ahead appears frozen in time. Its natural pose is almost eerie as it stares into the void."
    "Al bajar las escaleras, el esqueleto que hay delante parece congelado en el tiempo. Su postura natural es casi espeluznante mientras mira fijamente al vacío."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1774
translate spanish d11b130_818924a0:

    # St "Hey, friend... please stop staring at me like that."
    St "Ey, amigo... Por favor, deja de mirarme así."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1777
translate spanish d11b130_407f10ed:

    # St "Another note..."
    St "Otra nota..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1783
translate spanish d11b130_fb7f6527:

    # St "Let's see what's over here..."
    St "Veamos qué hay por aquí..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1784
translate spanish d11b130_cbc99431:

    # "{i}\"ID badges verification: 336753, 649319, 098770, 359588, 391801.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Verificación de placas de identificación: 336753, 649319, 098770, 359588, 391801.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1785
translate spanish d11b130_df022ce9:

    # "{i}\"Team 5 identification check completed and countersigned.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Comprobación de la identificación del equipo 5 completada y refrendada.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1786
translate spanish d11b130_c5a967d1:

    # "{i}\"Box 304087 must include the replacement unit EPB 36. Box to be locked and sealed before leaving the basement.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"La caja 304087 debe incluir la unidad de sustitución EPB 36. La caja debe estar cerrada y sellada antes de salir del Sótano.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1787
translate spanish d11b130_3deaab93:

    # "{i}\"Destination: the Station.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Destino: La Estación.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1788
translate spanish d11b130_cf257600:

    # St "They really wanted that box to be well looked after."
    St "Realmente querían que esa caja estuviera bien cuidada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1789
translate spanish d11b130_27c90307:

    # St "Station... isn't that what [persistent.dad] called the place where his old teacher holed up? That doesn't make much sense. There must be a different station, or maybe it means something else."
    St "La Estación... ¿No es así como [persistent.dad] llamaba al lugar donde se refugiaba su antiguo maestro? Eso no tiene mucho sentido. Debe haber una estación diferente, o tal vez signifique otra cosa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1798
translate spanish d11b134_6693eef3:

    # St "It's stable... good."
    St "Es estable... bien."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1801
translate spanish d11b134_a6b4a73d:

    # St "I am deep underground, in a dead place that has not been visited for probably a century, surrounded by dead people and deadly dust."
    St "Estoy en las profundidades del subsuelo, en un lugar muerto que no ha sido visitado desde hace probablemente un siglo, rodeado de gente muerta y polvo mortal."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1802
translate spanish d11b134_69458bce:

    # St "Just... don't think about it, [S]."
    St "Simplemente... no pienses en ello, [S]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1805
translate spanish d11b134_e70fcb98:

    # St "Let's see. Behind me, a way upstairs. I think I saw more skeletons there."
    St "Veamos. Detrás de mí, un camino hacia arriba. Creo que he visto más esqueletos allí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1808
translate spanish d11b134_48098fc3:

    # St "Ahead... giant... turbines?"
    St "Adelante... ¿turbinas... gigantes?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1809
translate spanish d11b134_af235262:

    # St "But what is that... glowing thing there?"
    St "Pero, ¿qué es esa... cosa brillante de ahí?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1810
translate spanish d11b134_f05f9bf0:

    # St "How can anything still be working, after this much time?"
    St "¿Cómo es posible que algo siga funcionando, después de tanto tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1811
translate spanish d11b134_2322bc9b:

    # St "Maybe that's what the reports were mentioning?"
    St "¿Tal vez eso es lo que mencionaban los informes?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1817
translate spanish d11b138_2e18f800:

    # St "This really is a bunker. This must be the air ventilation, or maybe a way to cool some machinery."
    St "Esto es realmente un búnker. Esto debe ser la ventilación del aire, o tal vez una forma de enfriar alguna maquinaria."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1818
translate spanish d11b138_b185fd0b:

    # St "I wonder if it was ever running, and for how long, after the bombs fell?"
    St "Me pregunto si llegó a funcionar, y durante cuánto tiempo, después de la caída de las bombas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1824
translate spanish d11b138_16bdf474:

    # St "Let's take a look."
    St "Echemos un vistazo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1827
translate spanish d11b138_5513f487:

    # "A green device just sits there, guarded by yet another deceased corpse. It seems to irradiate light, lighting up the floor below it."
    "Un artefacto verde se encuentra ahí, custodiado por otro cadáver difunto. Parece irradiar luz, iluminando el suelo bajo él."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1828
translate spanish d11b138_a1915ee7:

    # St "I have never seen anything like this. This might be one of those radioactive things [persistent.dad] warned me about."
    St "Nunca he visto nada como eso. Puede que sea una de esas cosas radiactivas de las que me advirtió [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1829
translate spanish d11b138_11741b89:

    # St "My counter better not be broken, because it doesn't seem to register anything in particular..."
    St "Más vale que mi contador no esté roto, porque no parece registrar nada en particular..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1830
translate spanish d11b138_6ef6c367:

    # St "I can get closer probably..."
    St "Probablemente pueda acercarme más..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1833
translate spanish d11b138_857c4669:

    # "Getting ever closer, the device's shape becomes clearer. Small, slim beams of light are emitted from the inside. It is put inside a box with some protective padding."
    "Acercándonos cada vez más, la forma del aparato se hace más clara. Del interior se desprenden pequeños y delgados haces de luz. Está metido dentro de una caja con un acolchado protector."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1836
translate spanish d11b138_eabb9359:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1837
translate spanish d11b138_2551b1ef:

    # "Fascinated by what is there to see, a question still comes up: how long has the item been here?"
    "Fascinada por lo que hay que ver, sigue surgiendo una pregunta: ¿Cuánto tiempo llevará aquí el objeto?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1838
translate spanish d11b138_f5b38fe8:

    # "Has it been glowing like this since this facility and its people found their ends? Why is it here at all, in this particular spot?"
    "¿Ha estado brillando así desde que esta instalación y su gente encontraron su fin? ¿Por qué está aquí, en este lugar concreto?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1839
translate spanish d11b138_751771bb:

    # St "You must be that important delivery that was mentioned on the board."
    St "Debes ser esa importante entrega que se mencionó en la pizarra."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1842
translate spanish d11b138_7cf41123:

    # St "And you... what did you leave behind?"
    St "Y tú... ¿Qué has dejado atrás?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1843
translate spanish d11b138_76769cbc:

    # "{i}\"Team 5 supervisor personal log: The EPB 11 was made under time constraints. I was made aware that the previous EPB was soon to be discarded.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Registro personal del supervisor del equipo 5: El EPB 11 se realizó por falta de tiempo. Se me hizo saber que el EPB anterior iba a ser descartado en breve.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1844
translate spanish d11b138_72f0f0df:

    # "{i}\"No explanation was given as to why. Faulty fuselage? Defective sealants? Has it simply run its course? The latter seems unlikely.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"No se explicó el motivo. ¿Fuselaje defectuoso? ¿Sellantes defectuosos? ¿Simplemente ha seguido su curso? Esto último parece poco probable.{/i}\""

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1845
translate spanish d11b138_4de29ccf:

    # "{i}\"I would have liked to have more information to understand the failings of the previous one, in order to avoid repeating them. As it is, we had to make EPB 11 in record time.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Me hubiera gustado tener más información para comprender los fallos del anterior, para evitar repetirlos. Tal y como están las cosas, tuvimos que hacer la EPB 11 en un tiempo récord.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1846
translate spanish d11b138_cabad942:

    # "{i}\"We did the best we could, but I want it officially recorded that we cannot take responsibility for any issues that might arise.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Hicimos lo mejor que pudimos, pero quiero que conste oficialmente que no podemos responsabilizarnos de los problemas que puedan surgir.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1847
translate spanish d11b138_3598568e:

    # "{i}\"The need for secrecy and the slow vetting process of qualified personnel also does not help.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"La necesidad de mantener el secreto y la lentitud del proceso de selección de personal cualificado tampoco ayudan.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1848
translate spanish d11b138_6619184a:

    # "{i}\"As it is, I know it will work, it will fully integrate with the Station and run the devices it is supposed to, both the Gate and the Horus System.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Tal y como está, sé que funcionará, se integrará completamente con la Estación y hará funcionar los dispositivos que debe, tanto la Puerta como el Sistema Horus.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1849
translate spanish d11b138_08a2423b:

    # "{i}\"I trust that with this, the Horus System will perform adequately and defend us from the long term consequences of the chemical fallout from the Scorched Earth Project. Durability however remains a potential issue.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Confío en que, con esto, el Sistema Horus funcione adecuadamente y nos defienda de las consecuencias a largo plazo de la lluvia química del Proyecto Tierra Arrasada. Sin embargo, la durabilidad sigue siendo un problema potencial.{/i}\""

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1852
translate spanish d11b138_c6176ea1:

    # St "[persistent.dad!c]'s old mentor was right. I can't think of anything that stands out more than this."
    St "El viejo mentor de [persistent.dad!c] tenía razón. No se me ocurre nada que destaque más que esto."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1853
translate spanish d11b138_2cb0c205:

    # St "This looks too valuable to be kept in the open. I will take a closer look at it once I am back in the shelter."
    St "Esto parece demasiado valioso para tenerlo a la vista. Lo miraré más de cerca cuando vuelva al refugio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1854
translate spanish d11b138_84af85b1:

    # St "I should also make a copy of this note in particular. I have a feeling that whatever that Abrax guy is trying to do, it's something big."
    St "También debería hacer una copia de esta nota en particular. Tengo la sensación de que, sea lo que sea lo que pretende ese tal Abrax, es algo grande."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1855
translate spanish d11b138_3c4ef68a:

    # St "Maybe we can find someone that can make more sense of this note."
    St "Tal vez podamos encontrar a alguien que pueda dar más sentido a esta nota."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1858
translate spanish d11b138_e38ebcc7:

    # "Placing the mysterious object in the bag was a simple task."
    "Colocar el objeto misterioso en la bolsa fue una tarea sencilla."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1859
translate spanish d11b138_d0615746:

    # "Time to head back."
    "Es hora de volver."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1862
translate spanish d11b138_7848927e:

    # St "I'm not sure how long this mask's filter will hold."
    St "No estoy segura de cuánto tiempo aguantará el filtro de esta máscara."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1865
translate spanish d11b138_d3675fd3:

    # St "I should go back. Careful now; no mistakes..."
    St "Debería volver. Cuidado ahora; no te equivoques..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1869
translate spanish d11b138_52be2c5b:

    # "After climbing out of the basement of the facility, the air inside the mask seemed to get thinner. There was not much time left, as the risk of exposure to the smog was too high."
    "Después de salir del sótano de la instalación, el aire del interior de la máscara parecía diluirse. No quedaba mucho tiempo, ya que el riesgo de exposición a la niebla tóxica era demasiado alta."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1871
translate spanish d11b138_0cd4de86:

    # "As all the notes indicated that this device was unique, it would work just fine as a prize for the expedition and it would be wiser to head back to the shelter."
    "Como todas las notas indicaban que este artefacto era único, funcionaría bien como premio para la expedición y sería más prudente volver al refugio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1875
translate spanish d11b138_a4810392:

    # "The way back was uneventful. No mutants or mummies were roaming the area."
    "El camino de vuelta fue sin incidentes. No había mutantes ni momias merodeando por la zona."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1876
translate spanish d11b138_008fe68b:

    # "The burning flashes of the anomaly, which could be felt even hundreds of meters away, was the only thing disturbing the quiet rest of the poor souls that met their fate in this part of the Zone."
    "Los destellos ardientes de la anomalía, que podían sentirse incluso a cientos de metros de distancia, era lo único que perturbaba el tranquilo descanso de las pobres almas que encontraron su destino en esta parte de la Zona."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1880
translate spanish d11b138_e25d00b7:

    # "The ruins next to the tree remained unaltered, the sky only showing its dark and grim self, without a hint of change."
    "Las ruinas junto al árbol permanecían inalteradas, el cielo sólo mostraba su ser oscuro y sombrío, sin un atisbo de cambio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1881
translate spanish d11b138_994e564b:

    # "There was no shelter this time around, and no host to take care of a traveller in need. Their history lost to the Zone, like so many other things."
    "Esta vez no había ningún refugio, ni ningún anfitrión que se ocupara de un viajero necesitado. Su historia se perdió en la zona, como tantas otras cosas."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1885
translate spanish d11b138_659d5026:

    # "The silver haired girl from the railway building was no longer there."
    "La chica de pelo plateado del edificio del ferrocarril ya no estaba allí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1886
translate spanish d11b138_6461624f:

    # "The table was empty; the only trace of their passage being the remains of the long since extinguished candles."
    "La mesa estaba vacía; el único rastro de su paso eran los restos de las velas apagadas hacía tiempo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1890
translate spanish d11b138_751a0086:

    # "Upon entering the old railway building, a sad spectacle met the eyes."
    "Al entrar en el viejo edificio del ferrocarril, un triste espectáculo se encontró con los ojos."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1891
translate spanish d11b138_43fd8756:

    # "Dangling from a rope, the lifeless body of that same milky haired girl, hung swaying gently in the breeze."
    "Colgando de una cuerda, el cuerpo sin vida de esa misma chica de pelo lechoso, colgaba meciéndose suavemente con la brisa."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1892
translate spanish d11b138_12ae4fba:

    # "Whatever shape of despair might have pushed her over the edge towards self-destruction, forever lost to the sands of time."
    "Cualquier forma de desesperación que la haya llevado al borde de la autodestrucción, se ha perdido para siempre en las arenas del tiempo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1893
translate spanish d11b138_8e742c63:

    # "With her lifeless body resting almost peacefully in the otherwise empty building, the girl was yet another victim of the bleakness that pervaded this place in it's eery silence."
    "Con su cuerpo sin vida descansando casi tranquilamente en el edificio, por lo demás vacío, la muchacha era otra víctima más de la desolación que impregnaba este lugar en su inquietante silencio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1894
translate spanish d11b138_7d314ce8:

    # "Would this be the fate of anyone who lingered too long in such a place?"
    "¿Sería éste el destino de quien se quedara demasiado tiempo en un lugar así?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1898
translate spanish d11b138_d38beea7:

    # "Leaving behind the open road and unsafe passages, the shelter finally came in sight."
    "Dejando atrás el camino abierto y los pasajes inseguros, el refugio se puso finalmente a la vista."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1899
translate spanish d11b138_1d4cccfa:

    # "A sense of trepidation and cautious optimism seems warranted now that at least one objective to this expedition seems to have been accomplished."
    "Una sensación de inquietud y un cauto optimismo parecen justificados ahora que al menos un objetivo de esta expedición parece haberse cumplido."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1908
translate spanish d11c_1319e7a5:

    # Z "Asha, go find that General guy and his girl."
    Z "Asha, ve a buscar a ese General y a su chica."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1909
translate spanish d11c_01709c1c:

    # Z "If you manage to find them alive, bring them here."
    Z "Si consigues encontrarlos vivos, tráelos aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1912
translate spanish d11c_2ac2cf4f:

    # As "We have them already captured, boss. I tried to not hurt them..."
    As "Ya los tenemos capturados, jefe. He intentado no hacerles daño..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1915
translate spanish d11c_d5cd4015:

    # As "...too much."
    As "... demasiado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1920
translate spanish d11c_ef91af82:

    # Z "Hey kid. Stop, look at me."
    Z "Ey, chica. Para, mírame."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1923
translate spanish d11c_f61c5220:

    # As "Hn?"
    As "¿Hn?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1924
translate spanish d11c_4622ee8c:

    # Z "Go find that General guy and his girl."
    Z "Ve a buscar a ese tipo del General y a su chica."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1925
translate spanish d11c_68de2edf:

    # Z "Bring them here. Understood?"
    Z "Tráelos aquí. ¿Entendido?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1928
translate spanish d11c_a770d63d:

    # As "Yes, boss!"
    As "¡Sí, jefe!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1933
translate spanish d11c_4f601925:

    # "She walks out of the building."
    "Ella abandona el edificio."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1934
translate spanish d11c_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Pasado un tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1937
translate spanish d11c_64d90ed7:

    # C "You're starting to piss me off. MOVE!"
    C "Estás empezando a cabrearme. ¡MUÉVETE!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1938
translate spanish d11c_db69a272:

    # C2 "Fuck you, don't touch my sister!"
    C2 "¡Joder, no toques a mi hermana!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1941
translate spanish d11c_b1b41b95:

    # C "I'll do much worse than touching her IF YOU DON'T MOVE YOUR. FAT. ASS. GOT IT?!"
    C "Haré algo mucho peor que tocarla SI NO MUEVE SU. GORDO. CULO. ¿LO ENTIENDES?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1942
translate spanish d11c_8e8444ef:

    # C2 "Don't, argh-"
    C2 "No lo hagas, argh-"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1946
translate spanish d11c_2af63058:

    # C "BOSS! I'M BAAAAACK!!!"
    C "¡JEFE! ¡¡¡HE VUEEEEELTO!!!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1950
translate spanish d11c_aaffa84e:

    # As "I couldn't resist roughing him up a little, buuut I promise he's fine."
    As "No pude resistirme a darle un poco de caña, pero te prometo que está bien."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1953
translate spanish d11c_f2bb33ad:

    # Zi "Urgh... what on earth is this thing."
    Zi "Urgh... ¿qué demonios es esa cosa?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1956
translate spanish d11c_f2de9456:

    # Zi "She's just asking for it, isn't she?"
    Zi "Ella se lo está buscando, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1959
translate spanish d11c_6fadb804:

    # Ky "There you are. Where did you two want to go, huh? Hide in the dunes?"
    Ky "Ahí estáis. ¿Dónde queríais ir? ¿Esconderos en las dunas?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1962
translate spanish d11c_32ab792b:

    # As "Ah... we're going to have our fun with you two.."
    As "Ah... vamos a divertirnos con vosotros dos.."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1963
translate spanish d11c_be30ac78:

    # As "I think I will carve out this one's tongue. He protests too much."
    As "Creo que le arrancaré la lengua a éste. Protesta demasiado."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1966
translate spanish d11c_d6a91e30:

    # Z "You're not talking so loud anymore. Nothing left to say?"
    Z "Ya no hablas tan alto. ¿No te queda nada que decir?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1967
translate spanish d11c_1545afe6:

    # As "Oh, believe me, he was shouting right until I kicked his ass in here just now."
    As "Oh, créeme, ha estado gritando hasta que le he dado una patada en el culo justo ahora."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1970
translate spanish d11c_2f5e9b11:

    # As "Couldn't stop screaming about revenge and punishment, actually. "
    As "No podía dejar de gritar sobre la venganza y el castigo, en realidad."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1974
translate spanish d11c_0a60fb24:

    # Zi "He was still convinced his allies, or his men or whatever, would come to fight for him."
    Zi "Sigue convencido de que sus aliados, o sus hombres o lo que sea, vendrán a luchar por él."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1975
translate spanish d11c_7643d139:

    # As "I don't think he understands how deep the shit is that he's in just now."
    As "No creo que haya comprendido lo profunda que es la mierda en la que está metido ahora."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1978
translate spanish d11c_2faa055b:

    # As "And what about you? Aren't you scared? Sitting here all quiet like, not saying a thing."
    As "¿Y tú qué? ¿No tienes miedo? Sentada aquí, tan callada, sin decir nada."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1981
translate spanish d11c_5e990086:

    # Kit "..."
    Kit "..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1982
translate spanish d11c_2a16f033:

    # As "Hey, bitch. Are you deaf?!"
    As "Ey, zorra. ¿Estás sorda?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1983
translate spanish d11c_8c2d49e9:

    # Gen "She's not deaf, fuck- damn it. She doesn't speak. Leave her alon-"
    Gen "Ella no es sorda, joder. No habla. Déjala en paz..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1984
translate spanish d11c_8232f03d:

    # Gen "agh-"
    Gen "agh-"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1985
translate spanish d11c_6ee02598:

    # Zi "Shut the fuck up or I'll cut your throat."
    Zi "Cierra la boca o te cortaré el cuello."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1988
translate spanish d11c_fb5357c5:

    # As "Is this bitch disrespecting me, looking all pretty and acting snooty, huh? Still thinking you're this shithole's little princess?!"
    As "¿Esta zorra me está faltando al respeto, poniéndose guapa y haciéndose la estirada? ¿Todavía piensas que eres la princesita de esta mierda?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1989
translate spanish d11c_4c6a8d89:

    # As "I think I may have to cut some sense into you..."
    As "Creo que tendré que hacerle entrar en razón..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1992
translate spanish d11c_b3980e0f:

    # Z "Alright, that's enough, Asha. I will take over from here."
    Z "Muy bien, es suficiente, Asha. Yo me encargaré a partir de aquí."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1993
translate spanish d11c_12d3085a:

    # "You stand beside Kitty and place your hand on her head..."
    "Te pones al lado de Kitty y colocas tu mano en su cabeza..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1996
translate spanish d11c_018e5b63:

    # Z "Hey, 'General'. Are you sure she's your sister? She's a delicate and pretty thing and you... well, you're you."
    Z "Ey, 'General'. ¿Estás seguro de que es tu hermana? Es una cosa delicada y bonita y tú... Bueno, tú eres tú."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:1999
translate spanish d11c_387fb54b:

    # Gen "Nghr-"
    Gen "Nghr-"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2000
translate spanish d11c_e8511340:

    # "He tries hard to break out off his chains..."
    "Se esfuerza por liberarse de sus cadenas..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2003
translate spanish d11c_e1ff736f:

    # Gen "Don't you dare touch her, you bald cockroach. I should've thrown you off the bridge when I had the chance!"
    Gen "No te atrevas a tocarla, cucaracha calva. ¡Debería haberte arrojado del puente cuando tuve la oportunidad!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2006
translate spanish d11c_9032faf3:

    # Zi "Shut it, shithead. It would be a shame if you died before I had my fun with you."
    Zi "Cállate, gilipollas. Sería una pena que murieras antes de que me divirtiera contigo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2007
translate spanish d11c_a48de2a3:

    # Ky "Or without seeing what's gonna happen to your sister, {i}*chuckles*{/i}."
    Ky "O sin ver lo que le va a pasarle a tu hermana, {i}*risilla*{/i}."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2010
translate spanish d11c_1fb48a51:

    # Gen "W-what do you mean with \"happen to her\"? What are you going to do?!"
    Gen "¿A-a qué te refieres con lo de \"pasarle\"? ¿Qué la vais a hacer?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2013
translate spanish d11c_9ed8d7a4:

    # Gen "You're not touching my Kitty. She's mine!! I own her!!"
    Gen "No vais a tocar a mi Kitty. ¡¡Ella es mía!! ¡¡Me pertenece!!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2016
translate spanish d11c_35cc6d14:

    # Ky "Aw, such a pity... I almost felt guilty, until you said what you just said."
    Ky "Ah, qué pena... Casi me sentí culpable, hasta que dijiste lo que acabas de decir."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2019
translate spanish d11c_022ddd4f:

    # Z "It doesn't look to me like she agrees with you. I wonder if she'll even care when you're gone..."
    Z "No me parece que esté de acuerdo contigo. Me pregunto si le importará cuando te hayas ido..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2022
translate spanish d11c_52960ca0:

    # Zi "I wonder what this fucker did to her that she doesn't speak a word. And what's with the blindfold anyway?"
    Zi "Me pregunto qué le habrá hecho este cabrón para que no diga ni una palabra. y de todas formas, ¿a qué viene la venda de los ojos?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2023
translate spanish d11c_ec6a93d2:

    # Zi "What did you do, gouge her eyes and cut her tongue out?! You're one fucked up brother."
    Zi "¿Qué has hecho, sacarle los ojos y cortarle la lengua? Eres un jodido hermano."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2026
translate spanish d11c_63267b02:

    # Gen "I didn't do shit! I would never harm her. That's just how we raised her, me and my Pa!"
    Gen "¡No he hecho una mierda! Nunca le haría daño. Así es como la criamos, mi padre y yo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2027
translate spanish d11c_e860579a:

    # Zi "How disappointing..."
    Zi "Qué decepción..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2028
translate spanish d11c_e48835f0:

    # Ky "Not everyone is as fucked in the head as you, Zion!"
    Ky "¡No todo el mundo está tan jodida de la cabeza como tú, Zion!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2029
translate spanish d11c_0b147a49:

    # Ky "The fuck you mean by raised her?!"
    Ky "¿A qué coño te refieres con lo de criarla?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2030
translate spanish d11c_2aaf545c:

    # Gen "She was born mute. The blindfold was just an extra thing we used to control her."
    Gen "Nació muda. La venda de los ojos era sólo una cosa extra que utilizamos para controlarla."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2031
translate spanish d11c_845aaf83:

    # Gen "A mute good for nothing runt that was only ever going to be useful if I turned her into a tool, but don't fucking tell me I hurt her. I wouldn't."
    Gen "Una renacuaja muda y buena para nada que sólo iba a ser útil si la convertía en una herramienta, pero no me digas que le hice daño. No lo haría."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2032
translate spanish d11c_43573d2b:

    # Ky "I take that back. This guy is even more fucked up than Asha on her period..."
    Ky "Retiro lo dicho. Este tipo está aún más jodido que Asha con la regla..."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2033
translate spanish d11c_51d0e646:

    # As "Hey! I heard that!"
    As "¡Ey! ¡He oído eso!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2036
translate spanish d11c_03aa9978:

    # Gen "Listen, you got this shithole place for yourself now, right? Fine! Take it."
    Gen "Escucha, ahora tienes este lugar de mierda para ti, ¿verdad? ¡Bien! Tómalo."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2037
translate spanish d11c_90296671:

    # Gen "Just give me back Kitty and let us leave! She's all I got. You won't hear from me again!"
    Gen "¡Devuélveme a Kitty y déjanos marchar! Ella es todo lo que tengo. ¡No volverás a saber de mí!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2038
translate spanish d11c_41331a20:

    # Ky "She's all you got? You're suddenly having feelings for her after blinding her?!"
    Ky "¿Ella es todo lo que tienes? ¿De repente sientes algo por ella después de haberla cegado?"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2039
translate spanish d11c_52a63577:

    # Gen "What the fuck are you talking about?! She's not blind, I told you I didn't lay a finger on her!! That's just part of her act."
    Gen "¿De qué coño estás hablando? No es ciega, ¡¡te he dicho que no la he puesto un dedo encima!! Eso es sólo parte de su actuación."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2040
translate spanish d11c_54e940f7:

    # Gen "She's the only capital I got, don't you get it? I can't go in the mines! I hate the cramped spaces in there!!"
    Gen "Ella es el único capital que tengo, ¿no lo entiendes? ¡No puedo entrar en las minas! ¡¡Odio los espacios reducidos de allí!!"

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2041
translate spanish d11c_9f9442d3:

    # Zi "Don't fret, asshole. I don't think you will have to worry about where to get your next meal from anytime soon, or ever."
    Zi "No te preocupes, imbécil. No creo que tengas que preocuparte de dónde conseguir tu próxima comida pronto, o nunca."

# game/scripts/day11.rpy:2044
